BoBoiBoy and his friends must protect his elemental powers from an ancient villain seeking to regain control and wreak cosmic havoc.
Covert security company Vanguard is the last hope of survival for an accountant after he is targeted by the world's deadliest mercenary organization.

Based on the true story of a pilot who had to ensure the safety of 128 passengers and crew members on the plane when its windshield became damaged mid-flight. The incident is regarded as one of the miracles in aviation history.

'Monster Cop' Ma Seok-do investigates an illegal online gambling business led by a former STS Baek and an IT genius CEO Chang. Ma proposes an unexpected alliance to Jang and begins hunting down the criminals.
A talented trainee pilot is given the opportunity to virtually test the latest fighter jet, which pushes him to his limits.

In the dark silence of the sea during World War II, the submarine USS Tiger Shark prowls on what should be a routine rescue mission. But for the shell-shocked crew, trapped together in the sub's narrow corridors and constricted spaces, this is about to become a journey into the sensory delusions, mental deceptions and runaway fears that lurk just below the surface of the ocean.

When Nancy is surfing on a secluded beach, she finds herself on the feeding ground of a great white shark. Though she is stranded only 200 yards from shore, survival proves to be the ultimate test of wills, requiring all of Nancy's ingenuity, resourcefulness, and fortitude.
A rescue unit within the Chinese Coast Guard are forced to overcome their personal differences to resolve a crisis.

A young artist gets stranded in an extensive, immaculate forest in western Ireland, where, after finding shelter, she becomes trapped alongside three strangers, stalked by mysterious creatures each night.

The world has been reduced to rubble by a massive earthquake. While no one knows for sure how far the ruins stretch, or what the cause of the earthquake may be, in the heart of Seoul there is only one apartment building left standing. It is called Hwang Gung Apartments. As time passes, outsiders start coming in to Hwang Gung Apartments trying to escape the extreme cold. Before long, the apartment residents are unable to cope with the increasing numbers. Feeling a threat to their very survival, the residents enact a special measure.
People binge eat and suffer from extreme thirst, which leads them to go crazy for water. They cannot control themselves because they are brainwashed by a parasite.

Syuhada, a naive has agreed to go hiking with her friends in Bukit Damai over the weekend. However, on the day of the incident, Syuhada felt strange when his friend did not show up. Assuming his friend had started the climb, she went into the forest and walked alone. Unfortunately, she fell into a hole which was 15 feet deep and not unable to get out of the hole.

The vacation of a group of youngsters turns into an endless horrifying nightmare after a losing bet forces them to spend a night on a deserted island.  As they stumble upon a mysterious abandoned village there, they accidentally break an old spell that was placed to restrain an antagonizing spirit trapped in the island. One by one, they are made to suffer the gripping and gruesome consequences of their mistakes,  infuriating an evil creature that needs human blood to stay alive. The only way out is in the hands of a girl who desperately needs to use her supernatural gift to untangle an unsettling history connected to a tainted cross-cultural love story.

The true story of technical troubles that scuttle the Apollo 13 lunar mission in 1970, risking the lives of astronaut Jim Lovell and his crew, with the failed journey turning into a thrilling saga of heroism. Drifting more than 200,000 miles from Earth, the astronauts work furiously with the ground crew to avert tragedy.
A look at the life of the astronaut, Neil Armstrong, and the legendary space mission that led him to become the first man to walk on the Moon on July 20, 1969.
When former Green Beret John Rambo is harassed by local law enforcement and arrested for vagrancy, he is forced to flee into the mountains and wage an escalating one-man war against his pursuers.
John Rambo is released from prison by the government for a top-secret covert mission to the last place on Earth he'd want to return - the jungles of Vietnam.

Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured.

Legend has it that hundreds of years ago, the world was plagued by a scourge – a giant snake with nine heads and a golden body. Often transforming into a woman as beautiful as a celestial fairy, Hydra wreaked havoc on the world and called herself Lady Golden Snake. People were terrified until Master Nan Hua appeared. He defeated the Hydra, beheaded her and trapped her immortal spirit in a divine sword.  Hundreds of years later, a mysterious demon broke into the Demonslayer's Hall, where the sword with the Golden Snake's spirit was kept, and stole the sacred relic. The young demoness Qu Ling was tasked with retrieving the sword, but due to her weak spiritual power, she was unable to resist the Golden Serpent and decided to seek the help of Bian Xiaoya, a demon hunter. Together they embark on a journey to retrieve the divine sword and save the world from the Hydra's second coming.

name: The Strange Snake Story in Shangtong Village

info.plot: Old times of the Tang Dynasty when a demonic dragon descended from the Qujiang Pond and the people of Chang'an became furious and desperate. Wang Xuan, a magistrate of the Yellow River, investigates the case secretly, but a plot to slaughter the city emerges, pointing to the saint's safety.

FBI agent Neville Flynn boards a flight from Honolulu, Hawaii to Los Angeles, escorting a key witness to testify against a mob boss at an upcoming trial. An on-board assassin releases a crate full of hundreds of deadly venomous snakes in an attempt to eliminate the witness. Flynn and a host of frightened passengers and crew must band together to survive the slithery threat.

The story of Pentecostal minister Glenn Summerford — a man accused of attempting to murder his wife with a rattlesnake in the sleepy town of Scottsboro, Alabama — and the investigation and trial that haunted Southern Appalachia for decades.

Peace Aod, a young gravedigger at Thamma Nakanimitr Temple, unearths an ancient gold anklet from a grave from the World War II period. He decides to pocket the anklet and falls prey to a curse that turns his skin into snake scales.

A barber seeks vengeance after his home is burglarized, cryptically telling police his "Lakshmi" has been taken, leaving them uncertain if it's a person or object, jeer at his request until they learn what they're really looking for.

Kumaresan, a police constable, gets recruited for an operation implanted to capture Perumal Vaathiyar, who leads a separatist group dedicated to fighting against the authorities for committing atrocities against innocent village women in the name of police interrogations.

During the British rule, Thangalaan, a fierce tribal leader, and his tribe assist Lord Clement, a British General, to trace gold in their village. While searching for the gold, the villagers earn the wrath of Aarathi, an apparent sorceress, who Thangalaan sets out to stop with all his might.
A man and his new love are caught in the middle of a dangerous conflict between a tough detective and a tyrannical politician.

Mathimaran, a police constable, wants to do something worthy of his job and stumbles upon an organ trafficking ring run by Durai that is exploiting immigrant labourers. But, with Durai's connections inside the force and in politics going deep, can the cop succeed?
A family from the underprivileged class is on the run after the teenaged son kills a rich man from the upper caste. Can the pacifist father be able to save his hot-blooded son?

The Chola kingdom is under threat from forces both internal and external, and with crown prince Aaditha Karikalan, his younger brother Arunmozhi Varman and the emperor, Sundara Cholar separated by situations, it is up to a messenger to ensure the safety of the kingdom. Can he succeed in his mission, especially with Karikalan's former girlfriend, Nandhini, plotting to bring down the entire Chola empire?
After being in jail for 14 years, Thilagavarman gets out of prison on parole. A cat-and-mouse chase unfolds as Nandhini, a tainted police officer zeroes in on him as suspect in a spate of murders
A honest cop tries to track down the brain behind a series of robberies and murders, but things turn personal when his family become pawns in the criminal's game.

Moorkkasaamy and Bhoominathan are divided by caste yet bound together by a friendship originated during their school days. Havoc reigns when Moorkkan’s father is attacked and all clues direct to Bhoomi being the perpetrator and the circumstances put the lives of two friends in a turmoil.

Amar is assigned to investigate a case of serial killings. When Amar investigates the case, he realizes it is not what it seems to be and following down this path will lead to nothing but war between everyone involved.

Sethupathi, an inspector, investigates the murder of a cop and finds that Vaathiyar, a big shot, is responsible for the killing. He arrests Vaathiyar, but an unfortunate incident that has a connection to the case he is investigating, puts his career in jeopardy.
Senapathy, an ex-freedom fighter, is angry. He is angry against the rampant corruption at every level of the bureaucracy. He will clean it up at any cost.

name: Pok Ya Cong Codei : Memburu Siti

info.plot: When Siti left, Pok Ya had no intention to look for her until he learns that she is pregnant with his child. The hunt for Siti is intensified when Pok Ya finds out Siti did not leave him…she was kidnapped!

Aidi, an application designer who has created BEBAS App, an important application used during the outbreak of the epidemic by providing user information for the purpose of providing current information. Jazman, an administrator of the company where Aidi worked, fired Aidi without any good reason. Aidi's grudge against Jazman continues to increase, especially when he sees the affection that Anggun, Aidi's dream girl, often has with Jazman. As a result of revenge, Aidi has stolen 27.7 million users' information from the BEBAS App and created a new character, namely Tengku Remy, in the virtual world to get to know Anggun. The data stolen by Aidi has also been sold to irresponsible parties in order to gain multiple profits. However, without realizing it, this illegal activity had led to big problems that would befall Aidi.

Kid is an anonymous young man who ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he is beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash. After years of suppressed rage, Kid discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the city’s sinister elite. As his childhood trauma boils over, his mysteriously scarred hands unleash an explosive campaign of retribution to settle the score with the men who took everything from him.
Framed and on the run, a former FBI agent must save his family from a blazing fire in the world's tallest building.

Chris and his girlfriend Rose go upstate to visit her parents for the weekend. At first, Chris reads the family's overly accommodating behavior as nervous attempts to deal with their daughter's interracial relationship, but as the weekend progresses, a series of increasingly disturbing discoveries lead him to a truth that he never could have imagined.

Five young New Yorkers throw their friend a going-away party the night that a monster the size of a skyscraper descends upon the city. Told from the point of view of their video camera, the film is a document of their attempt to survive the most surreal, horrifying event of their lives.

After a catastrophic car crash, a young woman wakes up in a survivalist's underground bunker, where he claims to have saved her from an apocalyptic attack that has left the outside world uninhabitable.

Villainous Gru lives up to his reputation as a despicable, deplorable and downright unlikable guy when he hatches a plan to steal the moon from the sky. But he has a tough time staying on task after three orphans land in his care.
Gru is recruited by the Anti-Villain League to help deal with a powerful new super criminal.

When a new threat capable of destroying the entire planet emerges, Optimus Prime and the Autobots must team up with a powerful faction known as the Maximals. With the fate of humanity hanging in the balance, humans Noah and Elena will do whatever it takes to help the Transformers as they engage in the ultimate battle to save Earth.

When Hong Kong Inspector Lee is summoned to Los Angeles to investigate a kidnapping, the FBI doesn't want any outside help and assigns cocky LAPD Detective James Carter to distract Lee from the case. Not content to watch the action from the sidelines, Lee and Carter form an unlikely partnership and investigate the case themselves.

It's vacation time for Carter as he finds himself alongside Lee in Hong Kong wishing for more excitement. While Carter wants to party and meet the ladies, Lee is out to track down a Triad gang lord who may be responsible for killing two men at the American Embassy. Things get complicated as the pair stumble onto a counterfeiting plot. The boys are soon up to their necks in fist fights and life-threatening situations. A trip back to the U.S. may provide the answers about the bombing, the counterfeiting, and the true allegiance of sexy customs agent Isabella.

After a botched assassination attempt, the mismatched duo finds themselves in Paris, struggling to retrieve a precious list of names, as the murderous crime syndicate's henchmen try their best to stop them. Once more, Lee and Carter must fight their way through dangerous gangsters; however, this time, the past has come back to haunt Lee. Will the boys get the job done once and for all?

While on a camping trip in order to reconnect, war veteran Colonel Lee Gunner must save his two sons from a gang of violent bikers when they're kidnapped after accidentally stumbling upon to a massive drug operation.

While working underground to fix a water main, Brooklyn plumbers—and brothers—Mario and Luigi are transported down a mysterious pipe and wander into a magical new world. But when the brothers are separated, Mario embarks on an epic quest to find Luigi.

When Branch's brother, Floyd, is kidnapped for his musical talents by a pair of nefarious pop-star villains, Branch and Poppy embark on a harrowing and emotional journey to reunite the other brothers and rescue Floyd from a fate even worse than pop-culture obscurity.

Ruby Gillman, a sweet and awkward high school student, discovers she's a direct descendant of the warrior kraken queens. The kraken are sworn to protect the oceans of the world against the vain, power-hungry mermaids. Destined to inherit the throne from her commanding grandmother, Ruby must use her newfound powers to protect those she loves most.

When the Valley of Peace is threatened, lazy Po the panda discovers his destiny as the "chosen one" and trains to become a kung fu hero, but transforming the unsleek slacker into a brave warrior won't be easy. It's up to Master Shifu and the Furious Five -- Tigress, Crane, Mantis, Viper and Monkey -- to give it a try.
Po and his friends fight to stop a peacock villain from conquering China with a deadly new weapon, but first the Dragon Warrior must come to terms with his past.

Power Spheras are high-tech robots carrying powers unimaginable. Coveted by many, these robots fled and hid themselves in various parts of the galaxy. One by one, Power Spheras have been hunted down and captured by those with ill intent. And now, their powers are used to wreak havoc and destruction throughout the universe. This is the tale of Earth's superhero, BoBoiBoy and his quest to save the Power Spheras and defend our galaxy.
BoBoiBoy and his crew respond to a distress call from an abandoned robot factory. When he's attacked by a lurking enemy, he unleashes a new Fusion power.
Despite their differences, BoBoiBoy aids the distress call's sender but clashing with their common for leaves him devastated.
As BoBoiBoy discovers the extent of his new powers, the crew tries to stop the Robo-dumpster from becoming a galaxy-hopping threat.
While the Robo-dumpster wreaks havoc, the gang teams up to stop it. To protect his friends and save Ochobot, BoBoiBoy activates a powerful new weapon.
Just as BoBoiBoy makes progress on wielding his Third Tier Elemental Powers, a shadowy newcomer captures his best friend and challenges him to a duel.
BoBoiBoy must make a difficult choice as he and his friends travel to the planet Windara and witness the cruel reign of the traitor Reramos.
BoBoiBoy and Fang crash-land in a desert, far from their crew. Soon, they fall into a trap set by Windara's inhabitants. But are they friends or foes?
Determined to stop Reramos from controlling Windara, BoBoiBoy and the crew sneak into Kupuri Castle to free Princess Kuputeri.
With little hope, Maripos and BoBoiBoy face the mighty General Karumbang in battle — but the crew acquires powerful artifacts to even the odds.
As Reramos transforms into a gigantic monstrous creature, BoBoiBoy must find a way to unleash the Tempest Power to stand a chance against him.

After the destruction of TAPOPS Station from Retak'ka's attack, BoBoiBoy and his friends return to Earth to await their next mission while continuing their studies.

Unexpectedly, an old foe returned with new evil tricks up his sleeves.

Planet Rimbara is a former colony of King Balakung, the original wielder of the Elemental Power of Darkwood/Timber who died at the hands of Retak'ka. A planet filled with jungles also holds many secrets.

Can BoBoiBoy unravel the secrets of King Balakung and obtain the Elemental power of Timber?

BoBoiBoy and friends return to Tuan Guru Gaharum only having 2 ingredients. However, BoBoiBoy was given another chance to prove his seriousness.

Their journey in Rimbara is nearing its end, but only one will be crowned champion. Who will inherit the knowledge of Sir Guru Gaharum from generation to generation? BoBoiBoy or Qually?

After receiving the Oakuat seed from Master Gaharum, BoBoiBoy is now eager to learn his Third Level Elemental Power. But BoBoiBoy's plan was successfully sniffed out by a cunning and scheming enemy. The fight between these two enemies leads them to a savage and wild world: Planet Kadruax!

After encountering the Tumbosar hordes on Planet Kadruax, BoBoiBoy and his friends try to escape in order to track down the valuable Power Sphere PasuBot that can help BoBoiBoy achieve his Third Level Elemental Power. But there's another surprise waiting for them in the wilderness of Kadruax, which could throw their plans into disarray!

BoBoiBoy Solar, BoBoiBoy Thorn, and Ying are in the Stone Pyramid, where the Power Sphere PlanterBot is stored. However, BoBoiBoy Thunderstorm, Gopal, and Yaya are still looking for a way to escape to avoid becoming prey to the Plantosaurs.

Can they save PlanterBot before Adu Du and Probe? Or did Adu Du manage to acquire the Power Sphere and release the latent power within him?

name: Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone

info.plot: Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.

name: Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets

info.plot: Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione’s magical abilities and courage.

name: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban

info.plot: Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.

name: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire

info.plot: When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.

name: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix

info.plot: Returning for his fifth year of study at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of students to defend themselves against the dark arts.

name: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince

info.plot: As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.

name: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1

info.plot: Harry, Ron and Hermione walk away from their last year at Hogwarts to find and destroy the remaining Horcruxes, putting an end to Voldemort's bid for immortality. But with Harry's beloved Dumbledore dead and Voldemort's unscrupulous Death Eaters on the loose, the world is more dangerous than ever.

name: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2

info.plot: Harry, Ron and Hermione continue their quest to vanquish the evil Voldemort once and for all. Just as things begin to look hopeless for the young wizards, Harry discovers a trio of magical objects that endow him with powers to rival Voldemort's formidable skills.

name: Harry Potter 20th Anniversary: Return to Hogwarts

info.plot: An enchanting making-of story told through all-new in-depth interviews and cast conversations, inviting fans on a magical first-person journey through one of the most beloved film franchises of all time.

name: Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them

info.plot: In 1926, Newt Scamander arrives at the Magical Congress of the United States of America with a magically expanded briefcase, which houses a number of dangerous creatures and their habitats. When the creatures escape from the briefcase, it sends the American wizarding authorities after Newt, and threatens to strain even further the state of magical and non-magical relations.

name: Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald

info.plot: Gellert Grindelwald has escaped imprisonment and has begun gathering followers to his cause—elevating wizards above all non-magical beings. The only one capable of putting a stop to him is the wizard he once called his closest friend, Albus Dumbledore. However, Dumbledore will need to seek help from the wizard who had thwarted Grindelwald once before, his former student Newt Scamander, who agrees to help, unaware of the dangers that lie ahead. Lines are drawn as love and loyalty are tested, even among the truest friends and family, in an increasingly divided wizarding world.
A bounty hunter in present day, learns about his previous life as a legendary warrior, when fate unites him with a mutant kid.

name: The Bad Guys: Reign of Chaos

info.plot: When a prison transport is attacked, dangerous criminals escape, plunging the city into chaos. To capture them, the police turn to an unconventional solution: assembling a team of notorious ex-cons, each with unique skills and brutal reputations. Led by veteran detective Oh Gu-tak, the ragtag crew—including the brawny gangster Park Woong-cheol and the slick con artist Kwak No-soon a.k.a. Jessica—must hunt down the fugitives before the city descends into complete lawlessness. As the lines between good and bad blur, alliances are tested in this high-octane action thriller filled with gritty fights, dark humor, and explosive showdowns.

Asian Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover several lost artifacts from the Old Summer Palace, the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese Zodiac animals which were sacked by the French and British armies from the imperial Summer Palace in Beijing in 1860. Assisted by a Chinese student & a Parisian lady, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

Sent into a drunken tailspin when his entire unit is killed by a gang of thrill-seeking punks, disgraced Hong Kong police inspector Wing needs help from his new rookie partner, with a troubled past of his own, to climb out of the bottle and track down the gang and its ruthless leader.
A washed-up stuntman and his stunt horse become an overnight social media sensation when their real-life fight with debt collectors goes viral.

After a family tragedy, three generations of the Deetz family return home to Winter River. Still haunted by Betelgeuse, Lydia's life is turned upside down when her teenage daughter, Astrid, accidentally opens the portal to the Afterlife.

As storm season intensifies, the paths of former storm chaser Kate Carter and reckless social-media superstar Tyler Owens collide when terrifying phenomena never seen before are unleashed. The pair and their competing teams find themselves squarely in the paths of multiple storm systems converging over central Oklahoma in the fight of their lives.

Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on and the skills to use them, The Expendables are the world’s last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table. But new team members with new styles and tactics are going to give “new blood” a whole new meaning.
After discovering she can see everyone's imaginary friends, a girl embarks on a magical adventure to reconnect forgotten imaginary friends with their kids.

The six-member crew of the International Space Station is tasked with studying a sample from Mars that may be the first proof of extra-terrestrial life, which proves more intelligent than ever expected.
A mysterious force knocks the moon from its orbit around Earth and sends it hurtling on a collision course with life as we know it.

Tensions flare in the near future aboard the International Space Station as a conflict breaks out on Earth. U.S. and Russian astronauts receive orders from the ground: take control of the station by any means necessary.

Dr. Ryan Stone, a brilliant medical engineer on her first Shuttle mission, with veteran astronaut Matt Kowalsky in command of his last flight before retiring. But on a seemingly routine spacewalk, disaster strikes. The Shuttle is destroyed, leaving Stone and Kowalsky completely alone-tethered to nothing but each other and spiraling out into the blackness of space. The deafening silence tells them they have lost any link to Earth and any chance for rescue. As fear turns to panic, every gulp of air eats away at what little oxygen is left. But the only way home may be to go further out into the terrifying expanse of space.

On August 16, 2013, the Supreme Court mandated the CIA to declassify files that had been kept secret for the past 75 years. Visual records of documented paranormal events were released to the public. The following incident took place in Gracefield, Quebec.

After depleting Earth's resources for centuries, humankind's survival requires an exodus to outer space. An international expedition is quickly formed to find a suitable new planet, but when plans go awry, the crew is suddenly stranded without power on a strange planet, where something unimaginable lies in wait.

Travel across the galaxy with John Sheridan as he unexpectedly finds himself transported through multiple timelines and alternate realities in a quest to find his way back home. Along the way he reunites with some familiar faces, while discovering cosmic new revelations about the history, purpose, and meaning of the Universe.

Thirty years after the events of the first film, a new blade runner, LAPD Officer K, unearths a long-buried secret that has the potential to plunge what's left of society into chaos. K's discovery leads him on a quest to find Rick Deckard, a former LAPD blade runner who has been missing for 30 years.

Using massive piloted robots to combat the alien threat, earth's survivors take the fight to the invading alien force lurking in the depths of the Pacific Ocean. Nearly defenseless in the face of the relentless enemy, the forces of mankind have no choice but to turn to two unlikely heroes who now stand as earth's final hope against the mounting apocalypse.

Mild-mannered Clark Kent works as a reporter at the Daily Planet alongside his crush: Lois Lane. Clark must summon his superhero alter-ego when the nefarious Lex Luthor launches a plan to take over the world.

Three escaped criminals from the planet Krypton, who have the same powers on Earth as Superman, test the Man of Steel's mettle. Led by General Zod, the Kryptonians take control of the White House and partner with Lex Luthor to destroy Superman and rule the world. But Superman, who made himself human in order to get closer to Lois, realizes he has a responsibility to save the planet.

name: Superman IV: The Quest for Peace

info.plot: With global superpowers engaged in an increasingly hostile arms race, Superman leads a crusade to rid the world of nuclear weapons. But Lex Luthor, recently sprung from jail, is declaring war on the Man of Steel and his quest to save the planet. Using a strand of Superman's hair, Luthor synthesizes a powerful ally known as Nuclear Man and ignites an epic battle spanning Earth and space.

Aiming to defeat the Man of Steel, wealthy executive Ross Webster hires bumbling but brilliant Gus Gorman to develop synthetic kryptonite, which yields some unexpected psychological effects in the third installment of the 1980s Superman franchise. Between rekindling romance with his high school sweetheart and saving himself, Superman must contend with a powerful supercomputer.

Superman returns to discover his 5-year absence has allowed Lex Luthor to walk free, and that those he was closest to felt abandoned and have moved on. Luthor plots his ultimate revenge that could see millions killed and change the face of the planet forever, as well as ridding himself of the Man of Steel.

A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.
Revolves around a precious postage stamp and attempts to steal, obtain it.
Wan Ibrahim needs to find an immediate solution to escape his uncle, Wan Usin, by selling some gold bars robbed by them, but the pressure and allegations passed by Wan Ibrahim are challenging him.

One of the most classic and revered stories of all time, Edgar Rice Burroughs' Tarzan returns to the big screen for a new generation. Tarzan and Jane face a mercenary army dispatched by the evil CEO of Greystoke Energies, a man who took over the company from Tarzan's parents, after they died in a plane crash in the African jungle.

HAQ is the action-packed story of two brothers gifted with special powers, one good and the other evil, who must either overcome or succumb to their own demons when they finally confront each other. Haq, the more caring and responsible of the two, was born with a gift of special powers passed down through his lineage. It is a gift nurtured and treasured by his family, used only when required.

name: Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One

info.plot: Ethan Hunt and his IMF team embark on their most dangerous mission yet: To track down a terrifying new weapon that threatens all of humanity before it falls into the wrong hands. With control of the future and the world's fate at stake and dark forces from Ethan's past closing in, a deadly race around the globe begins. Confronted by a mysterious, all-powerful enemy, Ethan must consider that nothing can matter more than his mission—not even the lives of those he cares about most.

When an IMF mission ends badly, the world is faced with dire consequences. As Ethan Hunt takes it upon himself to fulfill his original briefing, the CIA begin to question his loyalty and his motives. The IMF team find themselves in a race against time, hunted by assassins while trying to prevent a global catastrophe.

After a migrating duck family alights on their pond with thrilling tales of far-flung places, the Mallard family embarks on a family road trip, from New England, to New York City, to tropical Jamaica.

Someone is blackmailing the CIA by assassinating foreign journalists and making it look like the agency is responsible. As the world begins to unite against the U.S., the CIA must lure its most brilliant – and rebellious – operative out of retirement, forcing him to confront his checkered past while unraveling an international conspiracy.

Zee is a feared contract killer known as "the Queen of the Dead," but when she refuses to murder a young blind woman, she finds herself hunted both by criminal colleagues and a determined police detective.

Twenty years after modern civilization has been destroyed, Joel, a hardened survivor, is hired to smuggle Ellie, a 14-year-old girl, out of an oppressive quarantine zone. What starts as a small job soon becomes a brutal, heartbreaking journey, as they both must traverse the United States and depend on each other for survival.

episodes.name: When You're Lost in the Darkness

info.plot: 2003. As a parasitic fungal outbreak begins to ravage the country and the world, Joel Miller attempts to escape the escalating chaos with his daughter and brother. Twenty years later, a now hardened Joel and his partner Tess fight to survive under a totalitarian regime, while the insurgent Fireflies harbor a teenage girl with a unique gift.

In 2003, an Indonesian scientist makes a devastating discovery. In 2023, now outside of the quarantine zone, Joel and Tess clash over Ellie's fate as they navigate a long-abandoned Boston overrun with Infected.
Doomsday prepper Bill prepares to ride out the apocalypse alone...until a mysterious stranger upends his plans. Years later, Joel and Ellie seek Bill's guidance – and find themselves at a crossroads.

After a harrowing trek across a desolate United States, Joel and Ellie find themselves navigating a dangerous Kansas City on foot. Later, rebel leader Kathleen instigates a manhunt – one that pits her violent civilian militia against the world's best hope.

On the streets of a newly free Kansas City, Henry fights to protect his brother Sam from rebel soldiers who will stop at nothing to appease their ruthless leader. As her manhunt continues, Kathleen doubles down on her quest for revenge, while Ellie forms a meaningful friendship.
After months of traveling, Joel and Ellie receive a grave warning about what lies ahead. Later, Ellie learns more about Joel's past – while Joel tries his best to forget.

After being pursued by Infected, a pregnant Anna places her trust in a lifelong friend. Years later, Ellie is forced to grapple with the emotional toll of her journey, while Joel faces a devastating decision of his own.

As Joel fights to survive, Ellie’s struggle to save him stirs memories of her life in a FEDRA orphanage. Weeks before meeting Joel, Ellie recalls joining her best friend Riley for a night to remember… one that will change the course of both of their lives – and the fate of the world – forever.

After crossing paths with a vengeful group of survivors, Ellie's fighting spirit draws unwanted attention from its leader. Still battling for his life, a weakened Joel faces off with a hunting party out for blood.

The continuing story of Peacemaker – a compellingly vainglorious man who believes in peace at any cost, no matter how many people he has to kill to get it – in the aftermath of the events of “The Suicide Squad.”
After making a miraculous recovery, Peacemaker returns home–only to discover that his freedom comes at a price.
After Peacemaker’s hazardous escape, tension and mistrust build within the team. Later, as Peacemaker grapples with his new assignment, he receives a surprise visitor.

On their first official mission to assassinate suspected “butterflies,” Economos and Murn bond, and Peacemaker and Harcourt reach an understanding. But the whole job goes sideways with the arrival of Judomaster.
Following a somewhat successful mission, Murn recruits Vigilante. Meanwhile, after learning that the team helped land his father in prison, Peacemaker confronts his complicated past.

The team scouts the apparent hub for the aliens’ food supply, only to come face-to-face with a full-fledged invasion. Meanwhile, Auggie’s attempt to sell out his son to the police is complicated by Murn’s mysterious contact.
Murn reveals his deepest secret. Auggie is set free. The botched arrest of Peacemaker sends alien Goff into an unexpected new host.
Harcourt, Murn, and Adebayo find themselves surrounded by an alien force, while Peacemaker squares off against his father with help from Vigilante and Economos.
With Peacemaker and Adebayo at odds, can the team kill the cow once and for all – or will their fracture give the aliens the opening they need to complete its teleportation?

Ex Scotland Yard detective Millie-Jean Black returns to Kingston to work missing persons; soon finding herself on a quest to save a sister who won’t be saved, to find a boy who can’t be found, to solve a case that will blow her world apart and prove almost as tough to crack as Millie Black.

After decades in the U.K., ex-Scotland Yard detective Millie Black has returned home to Jamaica and joined the local police force. As she attempts to reconnect with her sibling, Millie and her partner Curtis are assigned the case of a missing schoolgirl that puts them on a collision course with both a powerful Kingston family and a U.K. detective.

With Curtis in the hospital and Hibiscus recovering from the attack on the Gully, Millie throws herself into her work. Initially suspicious of U.K. Detective Luke Holborn, Millie is compelled to team up with him when Janet's case leads to a disturbing discovery.

Millie reluctantly agrees to work with Holborn in the short term. Meanwhile, Hibiscus and Millie find a new balance in their relationship, and Curtis contemplates a change. Then, when Millie and Holborn make a breakthrough, Millie finds herself on a dangerous path.

Not knowing whom to trust, Millie goes rogue to get to the bottom of the Somervilles' criminal enterprise before Holborn can interfere. When Janet makes an unexpected decision, Millie must take extreme measures to protect the ones she loves and to find Romeo before it's too late.

In Kingston, Curtis faces the consequences of Millie's actions and must decide what matters most. Meanwhile, an undercover Millie arrives back in London. With few friends and scant resources, she must find and save Romeo before the mysterious "Lindo" can stop her.
The staff of Pittsburgh's Trauma Medical Center work around the clock to save lives in an overcrowded and underfunded emergency department.
While attempting to distract himself from the anniversary of his mentor's death, Dr. Robby introduces a fresh batch of interns to life in the ER.
Robby helps siblings navigate their elderly father's end of life care. Later, Samira fends off cops targeting a woman with a misunderstood condition.
Samira does her best to keep Whitaker on the right track. A teen overdose sparks conflict in the ER.
Bets are taken on the whereabouts of a stolen ambulance, while Santos learns a hard lesson, and Whitaker helps to tame “The Kraken.”
Santos and Collins each deal with moral quandaries. Samira’s careful approach earns praise from patients – and reproach from Robby.
While Robby handles an ultimatum from the hospital, Mel, Javadi, and Collins each handle unique mother-daughter dynamics.

Ten thousand years before the ascension of Paul Atreides, sisters Valya and Tula Harkonnen establish the fabled sect and female order that would become known as the Bene Gesserit to control the future of humankind.

On Wallach IX, young Valya Harkonnen promises Mother Superior Raquella that she'll protect the Sisterhood by putting one of their own on the Imperial Throne. Thirty years later, Valya faces a threat to her long-awaited plan.
After receiving word about events on Salusa Secundus, Valya brings Theodosia to the Imperial House to help manage the situation. Meanwhile, a reluctant Tula enlists Lila for a vital mission.

Following a tragedy, young Tula worries about being accepted despite her family name, while a skeptical Valya struggles with the decision to take the Sisterhood vow. Years later, Valya receives a message that confirms her suspicions.
As Tula attempts to understand the acolytes' shared dream, Valya sets her plan in motion to redeem House Harkonnen ahead of the Landsraad.
While Tula tries to keep her secret project from being discovered by the other Sisters, Desmond goes on a warpath to root out insurgents.
As Tula contends with his true identity, Valya's maneuvering leads her into an epic confrontation with an increasingly powerful Desmond.

Investigative journalist Eddie Brock attempts a comeback following a scandal, but accidentally becomes the host of Venom, a violent, super powerful alien symbiote. Soon, he must rely on his newfound powers to protect the world from a shadowy organization looking for a symbiote of their own.

Following the death of District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman assumes responsibility for Dent's crimes to protect the late attorney's reputation and is subsequently hunted by the Gotham City Police Department. Eight years later, Batman encounters the mysterious Selina Kyle and the villainous Bane, a new terrorist leader who overwhelms Gotham's finest. The Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.

After being murdered by corrupt colleagues in a covert government agency, Al Simmons makes a pact with the devil to be resurrected to see his beloved wife Wanda. In exchange for his return to Earth, Simmons agrees to lead Hell's Army in the destruction of mankind.

Nearly 5,000 years after he was bestowed with the almighty powers of the Egyptian gods—and imprisoned just as quickly—Black Adam is freed from his earthly tomb, ready to unleash his unique form of justice on the modern world.

All the residents of Kampong Pisang work together on cooking activities on the day before Raya. Husin returns to the village with Nelly's new lover until Ms. Chun is jealous and sulking because her love is rejected. Meanwhile, Barkoba was shocked by the presence of a former lover who had left him before because he married a man with the rank of factory manager. Pak Din was sad because his son suddenly could not return to the village to celebrate with him. Ms. Purnama carried suitcases and mattresses everywhere because of the silence. Pak Karim and Kak Som are happy because this is the first time they are celebrating without their child who is gone. As well as Daud M who has to work at night for the delivery of goods for the residents of Kampong Pisang who buy goods online.

Tells the story of a group of Kampong Pisang residents who are still committing misdeeds in the month of Ramadan. While Barkoba was enjoying a meal during the day in the bush, suddenly an incident occurred. He has been visited by the demon and brought Barkoba back to the past to recall every wrongdoing committed throughout his life. Barkoba ignores zakat, persecutes others, invites mischief and causes injury and death to Kiambang. Can Barkoba correct his past mistakes and return to the real world and succeed Barkoba in saving Kiambang.
As New York City is invaded by alien creatures who hunt by sound, a woman named Sam fights to survive with her cat.

Recently fired and desperate for work, a troubled young man named Mike agrees to take a position as a night security guard at an abandoned theme restaurant: Freddy Fazbear's Pizzeria. But he soon discovers that nothing at Freddy's is what it seems.
Bruce Banner, a genetics researcher with a tragic past, suffers massive radiation exposure in his laboratory that causes him to transform into a raging green monster when he gets angry.
The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.
Lara Croft, the fiercely independent daughter of a missing adventurer, must push herself beyond her limits when she finds herself on the island where her father disappeared.

Lawrence Talbot, an American man on a visit to Victorian London to make amends with his estranged father, gets bitten by a werewolf and, after a moonlight transformation, leaves him with a savage hunger for flesh.

Former race car driver Brent Magna is pitted against the clock. Desperately trying to save the life of his kidnapped wife, Brent commandeers a custom Ford Shelby GT500 Super Snake, taking it and its unwitting owner on a high-speed race against time, at the command of the mysterious villain holding his wife hostage.

Recent college grad Jaime Reyes returns home full of aspirations for his future, only to find that home is not quite as he left it. As he searches to find his purpose in the world, fate intervenes when Jaime unexpectedly finds himself in possession of an ancient relic of alien biotechnology: the Scarab.
During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.

Ford Brody, a Navy bomb expert, has just reunited with his family in San Francisco when he is forced to go to Japan to help his estranged father, Joe. Soon, both men are swept up in an escalating crisis when an ancient alpha predator arises from the sea to combat malevolent adversaries that threaten the survival of humanity. The creatures leave colossal destruction in their wake, as they make their way toward their final battleground: San Francisco.

Following the events of Captain America: Civil War, Peter Parker, with the help of his mentor Tony Stark, tries to balance his life as an ordinary high school student in Queens, New York City, with fighting crime as his superhero alter ego Spider-Man as a new threat, the Vulture, emerges.

Follows the heroic efforts of the crypto-zoological agency Monarch as its members face off against a battery of god-sized monsters, including the mighty Godzilla, who collides with Mothra, Rodan, and his ultimate nemesis, the three-headed King Ghidorah. When these ancient super-species, thought to be mere myths, rise again, they all vie for supremacy, leaving humanity's very existence hanging in the balance.
Explore the mysterious and dangerous home of the king of the apes as a team of explorers ventures deep inside the treacherous, primordial island.
In 1956 France, a priest is violently murdered, and Sister Irene begins to investigate. She once again comes face-to-face with a powerful evil.

When a massive, gilled monster emerges from the deep and tears through the city, the government scrambles to save its citizens.  A rag-tag team of volunteers cuts through a web of red tape to uncover the monster's weakness and its mysterious ties to a foreign superpower.  But time is not on their side - the greatest catastrophe to ever befall the world is about to evolve right before their very eyes.

When a man is offered a million dollars to play a game in which hunters try to kill him, he thinks he has found the perfect loophole: they can only attack when he’s alone. His only problem is that none of his friends or family believe the game is real.

"Hantu Bonceng" revolves around Amran (Zizan Raja Lawak) a delivery boy who often races in illegal drag races. It all started when Amran wins a race and is given a girl as his prize for winning the race. The girl rode with Amran to the port but Amran's bike was hit by the lorry after a turn in the junction. The girl died on the spot while Amran was brought to the hospital. The incident forces Amran to change as the ghost of the dead lady keeps haunting him every night. Amran feels the tension and asks his best friend Kunyit (Taiyuddin Bakar) for help.

Skilled cop Inspector Nuar discovers twins, Balqis and Qistina, mysteriously locked up in an abandoned house. He suddenly starts suffering a series of unexplained hauntings, and individuals linked to the case begin dying one by one. Nuar must now race against time to solve the dark mystery behind the two girls before it’s too late.
Sean Hall bercakap dengan CNN tentang pengambilgunaan budaya dalam industri muzik dan memberikan pandangan terhadap kes Taylor Swift.
Pada tahun 1956, seorang paderi dibunuh di Perancis, dan kejahatan berleluasa. Rahib wanita Irene berhadapan dengan biarawati syaitan, Valak.
Meg 2: The Trench menyelam ke perairan asing bersama Jason Statham dan Wu Jing yang mengetuai pasukan penyelidik meneroka lautan paling dalam.
Barry kembali ke masa lalu dan mengubah masa depan tanpa sengaja lalu menyebabkan dia terperangkap dalam realiti dengan Jeneral Zod.
Filem arahan Tina Satter, Sweeney sebagai Reality Winner, seorang wanita yang disabitkan kesalahan membocorkan laporan sulit mengenai campur tangan pilihan raya Rusia kepada media.
Pemandu trak, Kiran menemui Elena di dalam kontena. Dia merentas negara untuk bantu mencari keluarga gadis itu dan mempelajari perspektif baru.
Pertemuan semula dua beradik perempuan yang renggang dipendekkan oleh syaitan yang merasuki daging menyebabkan mereka terpaksa berjuang untuk terus hidup.
DUNGEONS & DRAGONS ialah filem pengembaraan epik adaptasi daripada francais permainan popular Hasbro.

Apabila Daughters of Atlas, trio dewa purba yang pendendam tiba di Bumi untuk mencari sihir yang dicuri daripada mereka sejak dahulu lagi, Billy—atau Shazam—dan keluarganya bertempur demi kuasa, nyawa, dan nasib dunia mereka.
Empat mangsa yang terselamat dari Woodsboro berpindah ke New York City, tetapi Ghostface kembali dan masih memburu mereka.

Di dalam waktu yang huru-hara, sebuah perkampungan terpencil diserang oleh puntianak (Phi Phob). Tiada siapa yang berani keluar rumah pada waktu malam. Malah polis juga dalam ketakutan dan enggan membantu. Khun Pan, seorang pegawai polis dan ahli sihir terkenal, dihantar untuk meyiasat kes itu. Perkampungan itu dikatakan telah menjadi sarang bagi dua orang penyamun, Sua Dum dan Sua Mahesuan.

name: The Weeknd: Live At Sofi Stadium

info.plot: Persembahan secara langsung bintang Kanada The Weeknd di Stadium SoFi, Los Angeles.

name: War Zone: Bear Grylls Meets President Zelenskyy

info.plot: Bear Grylls mengembara ke Ukraine untuk bertemu Volodymyr Zelenskyy, di Kiev, dan orang-orang berani yang tinggal di zon perang.

"Magic" Mike Lane kembali ke pentas selepas sekian lama menyepi lepas perniagaan yang gagal dan menyebabkan dia muflis seta menjadi pelayan bar di Florida. Mike ke London bersama seorang sosialit yang menawarkan sesuatu yang mustahil ditolak…

Dua beradik menjalankan hospital burung untuk menyelamatkan burung hitam yang cedera. Di salah satu bandar paling padat di dunia, "saudara burung" menjaga beribu-ribu makhluk memukau yang jatuh dari langit New Delhi yang dipenuhi asap.
Empat kawan baik memulakan perjalanan liar ke Super Bowl LI 2017 untuk menyaksikan wira mereka Tom Brady bermain.

Pengembaraan menyeronokkan tiga mumia Mesir yang tinggal di bandar rahsia bawah tanah di Mesir purba. Selepas beberapa peristiwa malang, mumia itu berakhir di London masa kini dan memulakan perjalanan yang aneh dan kelakar.

Apabila sepasang pembersih rumah yang bernasib Malang mendapati mereka ditugaskan untuk membersihkan rumah agam Lebron James semasa dia berada di luar negara, mereka memutuskan untuk membuat keputusan yang akan mengubah hidup mereka dengan mengadakan parti besar-besaran supaya mereka diingati dan mendapat wang. Apabila parti menjadi tak terkawal dan salah satu cincin kejuaraan Lebron hilang, mereka berdepan dengan satu malam liar yang takkan mereka lupakan.
Dengan harapan dapat berbaik semula dengan ayahnya yang ortodoks, anak kepada pengarah pengebumian Chasidic pulang ke rumah bersama isterinya yang sedang mengandung.

name: The Ringleader: The Case Of The Bling Ring

info.plot: Sebuah dokumentari tentang Rachel Lee, ketua pencuri Hollywood 2009 yang dikenali sebagai Bling Ring.

Bintang Filem Senyap, Bintang Muda, Eksekutif Penerbitan dan Pemuzik Sensasi perlu mengekalkan kerelevenan mereka pada zaman 1920-an di Hollywood semasa industri sedang melonjak ke hala tuju yang lebih baik.
Selepas mendapat hak penjagaan anak ke atas anak buahnya, Gemma meminta bantuan prototaip M3GAN.
Sudah tiba masanya untuk berparti dengan bintang besar Lizzo di Kia Forum, LA dengan penuh kepositifan, ketawa dan kasih sayang - mengingatkan kita semua tentang makna menjadi "100% wanita itu."

name: Puss In Boots: The Last Wish

info.plot: Kucing mahir pedang kegemaran semua telah kembali untuk pengembaraan baru di dalam dunia Shrek, apabila Puss in Boots membuat pencarian untuk mendapatkan Bintang Permintaan.
Sudan tiba masanya untuk menyambut perayaan dengan Tom dan Jerry! Dengan sihir, Jerry dan anak saudaranya, Tuffy, membuat tikus salji yang hidup secara ajaib!
Seorang bintang yang berjaya dengan menjadi dirinya sendiri. Dokumentari itu berkongsi kisah di sebalik permulaannya yang sederhana dan kepayahannya hingga kegemilangannya.
Sebuah drama autobiografi oleh pengarah legenda Steven Spielberg berdasarkan zaman kanak-kanaknya sendiri.

name: The Travelog: Hyoyeon & Sunny In Qatar

info.plot: Sertai Hyoyeon dan Sunny daripada kumpulan gadis K-pop terkemuka Korea, Girl's Generation, sambil mereka menikmati keindahan Timur Tengah.
Dua wartawan membongkar skandal Hollywood dan menggalakkan wanita untuk bersuara, menghancurkan sistem rasuah berdasarkan siasatan New York Times.

Fletch adalah suspek utama dalam kes pembunuhan semasa mencari koleksi seni yang dicuri. Dia mengalihkan tumpuannya kepada pelakon watak aneh untuk menentukan siapa pembunuhnya dan membersihkan namanya.

name: 2022 Rock & Roll Hall Of Fame Induction Ceremony

info.plot: Penerima anugerah 2022—Pat Benatar dan Neil Giraldo, Duran Duran, Eminem, Eurythmics, Dolly Parton, Lionel Richie dan Carly Simon—diberikan penghormatan.

name: Tad, The Lost Explorer And The Emerald Tablet

info.plot: Impian arkeologi Tad musnah sewaktu dia memecahkan sumpahan sarkofagus tanpa sengaja. Dia dan Sara berusaha untuk menamatkan sumpahan Tablet Emerald.

Dalam misi tempur terakhirnya merentasi pergunungan berceranggah di Afghanistan, jet juruterbang Tentera Udara Diraja Lt. Kate Sinclair (Charlotte Kirk) ditembak jatuh di atas salah satu kubu pemberontak paling berbahaya. Apabila pemberontak mengejarnya di lokasi nahas, dia mencari perlindungan di kubu bawah tanah yang telah lama ditinggalkan.
Kisah dewasa peribadi tentang kekuatan keluarga dan mengejar Impian Amerika.
TÁR mengisahkan perubahan kuasa dalam dunia moden, mengenai Lydia Tár, komposer dan ketua pemimpin wanita pertama orkestra terkenal Jerman.
Seorang lelaki berkulit putih membunuh 11 orang di pusat keagamaan Yahudi di Pittsburgh membuka isu krisis kebencian yang mengancam keselamatan kolektif kita.
George Clooney dan Julia Roberts bekerjasama sebagai bekas kekasih untuk menghalang anak perempuan mereka yang dilamun cinta daripada mengulangi kesilapan mereka.
Pertemuan semula keluarga di rumah agam terpencil menjadi maut kerana terperangkap dalam permainan ikhtiar hidup dan hanya seorang yang akan hidup.

name: Batman And Superman: Battle Of The Super Sons

info.plot: Jonathan Kent yang mengetahui dirinya mempunyai kuasa besar bergabung dengan Boy Wonder, Damian Wayne untuk menyelamatkan ayah-ayah mereka (Superman dan Batman) dalam dunia yang diserang oleh makhluk asing, Starro.
Halloween tiba dan musuh ingin membalas dendam terhadap Mystery, Inc.

Geram dengan percutian perayaan seasama ahli Batwheels, Batwing putuskan untuk pergi sendirian untuk menghalang rancangan jahat Mr. Freeze. Bagaimanapun, Batwing dan Batwheels saling bertelagah , meninggalkan Batwing sendirian apabila penjahat sejuk beku membekukan Bam, Buff, Bibi dan Redbird. Mampukah Batwing menghalang matlamat Mr. Freeze untuk membekukan seluruh Gotham dan hancurkan Krismas tanpa bantuan Batwheels?

Pengakhiran epik francais Halloween telah sampai kemuncaknya, setelah Laurie Strode (Jamie Lee Curts) bertembung dengan berdepan dengan Michael Myers buat  kali terakhir. Hanya salah satu daripada mereka yang akan terselamat.

Lin, kelulusan Harvard tanpa draf, mengejutkan teman pasukan dan para peminat serta memberi harapan kepada warga Asia di seluruh dunia setelah dia mendapat 38 mata di Madison Square Garden menentang Los Angeles Lakers. Ia lantas meneruskan kebangkitannya dan populariti “Linsanity.”
Kano yang ganas dan gila kuasa berazam untuk mengambil alih Earthrealm. Dibantu oleh trio askar upahan yang kejam, Black Dragon, dia memulakan serangan kejam dari bandar ke bandar.

Dr. Rose Cotter (Sosie Bacon) mendapat bayangan yang menakutkan selepas menyaksikan satu insiden pesakit yang mengerikan, dan mesti berdepan dengan masa lalunya untuk melarikan diri dari realitinya yang baru.
The Good House mengisahkan tentang perubahan hidup Hildy Good, seorang ejen hartanah New England dan keturunan ahli sihir Salem.

Sebuah cerita seram psikologi yang penuh dengan liku, Don’t Worry Darling, arahan pengarah Olivia Wilde yang mencungkil bakat Florence Pugh dan Harry Styles, juga dikelilingi dengan watak-watak yang menarik.
Bruce Cogburn, seorang pengarang mula menerima surat daripada peminat yang taksub. Dia menjumpai teka-teki yang bahaya ketika mencari orang yang menghantar mesej rahsia itu.

Apabila penguat kuasa rusuhan terkemuka Miami mendapati wanita bosnya telah menceburkan diri ke dalam pemerdagangan seksual siber, dia memutuskan untuk mengorbankan segala-galanya untuk menyelamatkan seorang remaja muda yang melarikan diri.

Sebuah komedi menarik dibintangi oleh Jon Hamm sebagai Fletch yang menawan, yang menjadi suspek utama dalam kes pembunuhan semasa mencari koleksi seni yang dicuri. Dia meneliti ramai orang untuk mencari dalangnya untuk membersihkan namanya.
MOONAGE DAYDREAM merangkumi kisah hidup dan kebijaksanaan David Bowie, salah satu artis yang terkenal dan berpengaruh yang pernah wujud.
Sekumpulan rakan kolej menyewa rumah pintar untuk berpesta hujung minggu. Tapi, mereka mula menyedari bahawa Margaux, sistem AI termaju rumah itu, mempunyai reka bentuk jahat untuk mereka.
Emma tinggal bersama mak ciknya selepas kematian bapanya. Suaminya mengesyaki Emma dan seorang gadis sekolah baru mengetahui rahsianya.

Seorang penjenayah kecil sedang melarikan diri dengan beg yang penuh dengan wang tunai dan kokain. Dia sangat keliru dan cedera parah. Dengan peluru di dalam perutnya dia kesuntukan masa. CEPAT. Jika dia tidak mendapat pemindahan darah dalam beberapa jam akan datang, dia akan mati. Dia akan mati lebih cepat jika VIC , baron dadah wanita Mexico yang menjadi manga curinya menangkapnya terlebih dulu. Dia menaiki bas sehala ke luar bandar. Rakan-rakannya, Mac dan JJ tak begitu bernasib baik. Freddy mencuba setiap helah dan setiap hubungan yang dia ada untuk membawanya keluar daripada situasi ini. Bas menjadi tempt penyeksaannya. Di dalam bas, salah seorang penumpang kelihatan tak macam yang mereka nampak manakala seorang lagi, seorang gadis remaja, berjalan sendiri ke sudut berbahaya dan gelap. Apabila masa Freddy habis, dia telah menghadapi syaitannya.

Memecut di padang pasir Maghribi untuk menghadiri pesta hujung minggu rakan lama, orang kaya London David dan Jo Henninger (Ralph Fiennes dan Jessica Chastain) mengalami kemalangan tragis dengan seorang remaja lelaki tempatan.

name: Honk For Jesus, Save Your Soul

info.plot: Selepas kejadian skandal yang besar, wanita pertama Gereja Baptist Selatan dan suaminya, seorang pastor, cuba untuk membina semula jemaah mereka yang hampir pupus. Ia merupakan kemunculan semula yang terbesar di dalam komoditi keagamaan.
John McEnroe, seorang pemain tenis yang berjaya mengubah sukan ini tapi terkenal dengan sifatnya yang panas baran, berang dan kata-katanya.
Sebuah filem seram baru yang mendebarkan tentang seorang ayah dan dua anak perempuannya yang diburu oleh singa buas di Afrika Selatan.
Seorang anak muda menemukan markas rahasia dari superhero terkuat di dunia di bawah rumahnya dan ia harus mempertahankannya dengan teman-temannya terhadap serangan lawan.

Bagi kawan baik Becky dan Hunter, hidup adalah tentang menakluki ketakutan dan melangkaui had. Selepas mereka mendaki 2,000 kaki ke puncak menara radio yang terpencil, mereka terkandas tanpa jalan ke bawah.
Manusia tiruan mempersoalkan realiti apabila kenangan kehidupan lampau muncul semula.

Bintang komedi berdiri Jo Koy (Jo Koy: In His Elements, Jo Koy: Comin' in Hot) berlakon sebagai seorang lelaki yang pulang sempena perayaan Easter dengan keluarganya yang kecoh dalam filem untuk masyarakat Filipina-Amerika.

Dalam DC League of Super-Pets, Krypto Si Anjing Super dan Superman adalah kawan baik, berkongsi kuasa besar yang sama dan membanteras jenayah di Metropolis bersama-sama. Apabila Superman dan semua ahli Justice League diculik, Krypto perlu yakinkan kumpulan perlindungan jalanan. Ace Si Anjing, PB Si Khinzir, Merton Si Penyu dan Chip Si Tupai untuk menguasai kuasa baru mereka dan membantunya menyelamatkan semua adiwira.
Seorang adi wira kembali ke dunia untuk menebus dirinya.

Dalam Filem DC Universe yang mendebarkan ini, Green Lantern terbaru di bumi akan muncul! Apabila Cincin Kuasa dianugerahkan kepada bekas Marin John Stewart, dia berhadapan dengan misi yang mengubah hidupnya.
The Looney Builders prepare to host a big holiday lights festival in Looneyburg Park when an unexpected snowstorm prevents Looneyburgers from attending.
Filem ganas baru karya pemenang Academy Award® Jordan Peele ("Get Out," "Us"), dibintangi oleh Daniel Kaluuya, Keke Palmer dan Steven Yeun.

Selepas bekerja, kelaparan dan berjudi untuk mengumpul dana untuk mengejar impiannya, Pn. Harris memulakan pengembaraan ke Paris yang bukan sahaja mengubah pandangannya sendiri, tetapi juga masa depan House of Dior.
Filem ini mempersembahkan potret Sir Ranulph Fiennes yang menarik, menggabungkan masa lalu dan masa kini melalui arkib dan dokumentari.
Empat wartawan di negara demokrasi berdepan dengan bahaya ketika cuba membongkar mereka yang berkuasa, menunjukkan kepentingan kebebasan akhbar.
Pada 1970-an, Gru membesar di pinggir bandar. Seorang peminat kumpulan super penjahat yang dikenali sebagai Vicious 6, Gru merancang untuk menjadi cukup jahat untuk menyertai mereka.
BJ Novak dan Blumhouse Productions bekerjasama dalam filem arahan pertama Novak, audio siar-wartawan yang menyiasat kematian bekas kekasihnya.

Dari pencalonan Oscar pembikin filem Baz Luhrmann, terbitnya drama Warner Bros Pictures, Elvis, yang dibintangi oleh Austin Butler dan pemenang Oscar, Tom Hanks. Filem ini mengisahkan kehidupan dan muzik Elvis Presley (Butler), yang dilihat melalui hubungannya yang rumit dengan pengurusnya, Kolonel Tom Parker (Hanks). Kisah ini tentang kerumitan dinamik di antara Presley dan Parker selama 20 tahun, dari kebangkitan Presley ke arah kemasyhuran sehingga menjadi bintang, dengan landskap budaya yang berkembang dan kehilangan rasa tidak bersalah di Amerika. Sepanjang perjalanan itu, terdapat orang paling penting dan berpengaruh dalam hidup Elvis, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge).

Finney, budak lelaki berusia 13 tahun yang pemalu tetapi pandai, diculik oleh pembunuh sadis dan terperangkap di ruang bawah tanah kalis bunyi. Apabila telefon yang terputus di dinding mula berdering, Finney mendapati dia dapat mendengar suara mangsa pembunuh sebelum ini.
Selepas kematian mengejut bidan mereka, sepasang suami isteri L.A. mengupah anaknya untuk menjadi pembantu bidan yang tinggal bersama mereka.
Brian, seorang pencipta yang keseorangan membina robot untuk syarikat, tetapi dia terpaksa berdepan dengan lebih banyak daripada yang dia sangka dalam komedi yang menawan ini.

A romantic comedy-drama in which an uptight father (Andy Garcia) tries to come to grips with his daughter's upcoming wedding, framed through the prism of multiple relationships within a big, sprawling Cuban-American Latino clan. Remake of the 1950 film of the same name, which had another hit version in 1991 starring Steve Martin.

Kisah benar yang menakjubkan tentang bagaimana pesara Jerry Selbee menemui kelemahan matematik dalam loteri Massachusetts dan, dengan bantuan isterinya, Marge, memenangi 27 juta dolar dan menggunakan wang itu untuk memulihkan bandar kecil mereka di Michigan.

Tweety berkuasa dan bertanggungjawab selepas mengambil takhta dalam filem baru ini. Apabila ratu pulau hilang, Tweety tiba-tiba menjadi yang seterusnya untuk mengambil takhta. Kawan-kawan Tweety termasuk Nenek bermotosikal dan Sylvester yang licik, yang kesetiaannya diuji apabila dia menemui rancangan jahat untuk menghapuskan Tweety buat selamanya! Bulu-bulu akan berterbangan dalam kisah lucu ini yang menunjukkan kerabat diraja dan kesetiaan boleh datang dalam pelbagai bentuk dan saiz.
Edward Buckles, Jr. mendokumentasikan kisah rakan sebayanya yang terselamat daripada ribut Katrina semasa dia berumur 12 tahun di New Orleans.
Empat tahun selepas kemusnahan Isla Nublar, dinosaur kini hidup bersama manusia di seluruh dunia dan mengancam untuk mengatasi manusia sebagai pemangsa puncak planet ini.
Pada tahun 1972, polis Chicago menahan tujuh wanita yang membentuk rangkaian rahsia bernama Jane, yang menyediakan tempat pengguguran haram.

Seorang Marsyal AS melindungi saksi – isteri kepada bos sindiket jenayah – di Afrika Selatan. Mereka perlu bekerjasama dan yakin antara satu sama lain untuk menyelamatkan diri dan menghentikan jenayah.
Emma dan Scarlett, dua pontianak nakal bergabung tenaga untuk menyelamatkan adik mereka apabila dia melarikan diri daripada cubaan penculikan yang mengorbankan ibu bapa mereka sebelum ini.

Selepas 30 tahun, Maverick (Tom Cruise) masih bergiat aktif sebagai juruterbang tentera laut atasan, tetapi dia harus mendepani sejarah ngerinya apabila dia mengetuai anggota elit baru TOP GUN dalam misi yang memerlukan pengorbanan daripada para juruterbang yang terlibat.
This documentary film follows Russian opposition leader, Alexey Navalny, through his political rise, attempted assassination and search to uncover the truth.

name: Teen Titans Go! & Dc Super Hero Girls: Mayhem In The Multiverse

info.plot: Apa yang anda dapat jika gabungkan DC Super Hero Girls, Legion Doom dan Teen Titans Go! dengan ratu Kriptoni? Akan berlakulah huru-hara! Dengan pertolongan azimat dari Kripton, Lex Luthor menyatukan pasukan adiwira untuk menangkap semua adi wira bumi dan meninggalkan hanya DC Super Hero Girls untuk hentikan Legion Doom. Gadis itu perlu menyeberang dimensi untuk menyelamatkan adi wira lain daripada Zon Hantu, tapi mereka tiba di alam semesta lain. Saksikan perlawanan alam semesta DC untuk menyelamatkan dunia dengan peristiwa epik!
Fenomena di seluruh dunia bersambung dalam "Downton Abbey 2", susulan kepada sambungan filem cereka popular 2019 daripada siri televisyen popular di seluruh dunia.
“Firestarter" mengisahkan seorang gadis muda (Ryan Kiera Armstrong) yang mempunyai pyrokinesis, menarik perhatian agensi rahsia kerajaan yang ingin mengeksploitasi kuasanya sebagai senjata.

name: Dc Showcase: Constantine - The House Of Mystery

info.plot: Selepas menghalang Perang Apokalips, John Constantine, yang terperangkap dalam Rumah Misteri, melalui kitaran tanpa henti yang sentiasa berakhir dengan kematiannya. Bolehkah dia melarikan diri dari neraka ini?

Beberapa minggu selepas serangan besar ke atas Fortress, serangan baru dimulakan dan ejen CIA yang telah bersara, Robert Michaels berdepan dengan seseorang yang dikenali yang dia sangka dia takkan jumpa lagi.
Alex Lewis ialah seorang pembunuh upahan pakar. Apabila Alex enggan menyelesaikan tugas untuk organisasi jenayah berbahaya, dia menjadi sasaran dan perlu memburu mereka yang nak dia mati.
Daripada pengarah Robert Eggers, muncullah The Northman, sebuah filem aksi tentang putera Viking muda membalas dendam untuk pembunuhan ayahnya.
Kru penjenayah haiwan yang hebat akan cuba menjayakan penipuan mereka yang paling mencabar iaitu menjadi model rakyat.

name: Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets Of Dumbledore

info.plot: Profesor Albus Dumbledore tahu ahli sihir Jahat yang berkuasa Gellert Grindelwald sedang bertindak untuk menguasai dunia ahli sihir.

name: Tony Hawk: Until The Wheels Fall Off

info.plot: Filem ini adalah tentang kehidupan dan kerjaya ikonik Hawk, dan hubungannya dengan sukan yang sudah sebati dengannya selama beberapa dekad.
Dalam filem aksi yang diarahkan oleh Michael Bay ini, adik-beradik terdesak merampas ambulans selepas rompakan mereka tak berjaya, dan menjadi pelarian paling luar biasa yang pernah dilihat di LA.

Landak biru kegemaran orang ramai kembali lagi! Dr. Robotnik kembali kali ini bersama teman baharu, Knuckles, mencari zamrud yang berkuasa. Sonic dan kawannya, Tails menghentikan rancangan Dr. Robotnik sebelum terlambat.

Stephen Fry embarks on an incredible journey to discover the stories behind some of the world's most fantastic beasts. Whether digging for dragons, or meeting distant relatives of the unicorn, Stephen reveals the real-life beasts that have inspired some of the greatest myths and legends in history, story-telling and film.

Apabila tugasan pertamanya tidak berjaya, seorang bekas tentera elit diburu, terperangkap dalam konspirasi dan berjuang untuk terus hidup untuk pulang ke rumah dan mendedahkan motif sebenar orang yang mengkhianatinya.
Filem aksi cereka sains yang lucu tentang wanita Cina Amerika yang tak mampu membayar cukai dan mendapat tahu dia mampu menyelamatkan seluruh dunia pelbagai.

Selepas diculik oleh pemburu harta karun yang jahat, seorang novelis romantik yang berjaya dipaksa bergabung dengan model muka hadapannya kerana mereka terperangkap di dalam hutan yang penuh pengembaraan.

name: Super Greed: The Fight For Football

info.plot: Super Greed: The Fight for Football menceritakan kisah dalaman yang dramatik tentang liga yang telah ditakdirkan musnah melalui mata mereka yang membantu menjatuhkannya.

Selepas kerjaya sedekad yang penuh dengan kecederaan dan peluang yang terlepas, Michael Bisping, ahli middleweight UFC yang berusia 38 tahun akhirnya mendapat haknya, dan dia bercadang untuk keluar menjadi lebih baik.

"The Outfit" mengikuti kehidupan seorang tukang jahit Inggeris yang pernah menghasilkan sut di Savile Row di London yang terkenal di dunia. Selepas berlaku tragedi yang agak peribadi, dia berpindah ke Chicago, mengendalikan kedai tukang jahit kecil di bahagian pinggir bandar. Dia membuat pakaian cantik untuk satu-satunya orang di kawasan itu yang mampu membelinya. Keluarga samseng ganas.

name: Making Of The Last Of Us

info.plot: Dokumentari penuh yang memaparkan usaha di sebalik tabir yang gerun dalam pembikinan siri popular The Last Of Us.
Apabila pembunuh bersiri sadis mula membunuh ahli politik utama di Gotham, Batman menyiasat rasuah tersembunyi di bandar itu dan mencari pelakunya.

Matsuri Takabayashi yang berusia 20 tahun mengetahui bahawa dia hanya ada sepuluh tahun untuk hidup akibat penyakit yang tidak dapat diubati. Dia memutuskan untuk tidak memikirkan hidupnya dan tidak jatuh cinta, tetapi dia bertemu Kazuto Manabe di perjumpaan sekolah.

Selepas melarikan diri dari perhambaan pada usia 20 tahun, Frederick Douglass menjadi lelaki kulit hitam yang paling terkenal pada abad ke-19 kerana kata-katanya. Dokumentari HBO ini mengenai kebangkitan beliau daripada seorang pejuang yang bersemangat kepada negarawan yang tenang.

Ray, bekas penjenayah, sedang mengelak daripada pembunuh kejam. Dia mencari perlindungan dengan orang yang baik. Tapi sebenarnya dia telah terlibat dengan seseorang yang lebih berbahaya daripada pembunuh yang mengejarnya.

Mengumpul hampir 20 bilion dolar sepanjang separuh abad yang lalu dan mengungguli beberapa tawaran perniagaan paling hebat pada zaman kita, Carl Icahn ialah seorang perunding dan pakar strategi yang digeruni dalam seni pengambilalihan dan pelaburan korporat.

Penuh dengan lagu asli oleh Jennifer Lopez dan bintang muzik Latin global Maluma, "Marry Me" menampilkan Lopez sebagai bintang muzikal Kat Valdez dan Owen Wilson sebagai Charlie Gilbert, seorang guru matematik—orang yang tidak dikenali yang bersetuju untuk berkahwin dan kemudian mengenali satu sama lain . Percintaan yang agak mustahil tentang dua orang berbeza yang mencari sesuatu yang nyata dalam dunia yang nilainya berdasarkan suka dan pengikut, "Marry Me" ialah kisah cinta moden tentang selebriti, perkahwinan dan media sosial.

After an agoraphobic Seattle tech worker (Kravitz) discovers recorded evidence of a violent crime during an ordinary data stream review, she tries reporting it up the chain of command at her company. Met with resistance and bureaucracy, she realises that in order to get involved she will have to do the thing she fears the most — leave the safety of her apartment and step out into the open onto the streets that absolutely terrify her.Directed by Steven Soderbergh (Erin Brockovich, Ocean’s Elevan, Contagion). Written by David Koepp (Jurassic Park, Panic Room, Spider-Man).

Selina Kyle, the Catwoman, is simply trying to steal the world's most valuable emerald. Unfortunately, that emerald is currently in the possession of Leviathan, the world's foremost criminal empire. Who knew a little thing like stealing Leviathan's property would result in a price being put on Selina's head? Now, the bad guys and the good guys are hot on the Cat's tail. Can our famously infamous feline slink her way clear of this international mess? Only one way to find out...
Bulan sedang menuju ke bumi dengan pelanggaran. Tiga orang adi wira meneruskan misi ke angkasa lepas untuk menghentikan malapetaka, tapi mereka dapat tahu yang bulan bukan seperti yang kita fikir.

name: And Just Like That... The Documentary

info.plot: A one-off documentary, chronicling how the new chapter of the beloved hit series "Sex And The City", came to be.
High schooler Vada navigates the emotional fallout she experiences in the wake of a school tragedy. Relationships with her family and friends, as well as her view of the world, are forever altered.

Difilem secara keseluruhannya melalui dunia reality maya, dokumentari ini memaparkan keterujaan dan hubungan rapat gerakan budaya yang semakin berkembang. Ia menunjukkan hubungan dalam talian yang kuat di dalam dunia yang penuh denganpengasingan.

Claire, wanita muda bercita-cita tinggi mempunyai segala-galanya - jawatan baru di agensi hartanah terkemuka dan cinta baru. Tetapi hidupnya berubah apabila dia telah jatuh cinta dengan isteri bosnya, terperangkap dalam jaringan niat jahat.
25 tahun selepas pembunuhan bersiri yang asal di Woodsboro, pembunuh baru muncul, dan Sidney Prescott perlu kembali untuk menyiasat perkara sebenar.
Ejen CIA yang telah bersara dan anaknya telah dikepung di dalam bunker berteknologi tinggi oleh sekumpulan penjenayah. Mampukah dinding besi dan senjata canggih menghalang mereka?

name: Harry Potter 20Th Anniversary: Return To Hogwarts

info.plot: Daniel Radcliffe, Rupert Grint and Emma Watson join filmmaker Chris Columbus and other esteemed cast members across all eight Harry Potter films as they travel back to Hogwarts for the first time to celebrate the anniversary of the franchise's first film, Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone, which premiered 20 years ago. The retrospective special  will tell an enchanting making-of story through all-new in-depth Harry Potter 20th Anniversary: Return to Hogwartsinterviews and cast conversations, inviting fans on a magical first person journey through one of the most beloved film franchises of all time.

name: The Electrical Life Of Louis Wain

info.plot: Sebuah kisah benar tentang pelukis British, Louis Wain, yang suka bermain-main. Kadang-kadang, lukisannya yang psikedelik dapat membantu mengubah persepsi orang ramai terhadap kucing.
Sebuah dokumentari lucu dan intim yang meraikan kehidupan dan warisan mendiang pelakon, penulis, dan penerbit Bob Einstein.

Filem keempat yang telah lama ditunggu-tunggu dalam francais aksi, yang menyatukan semula Keanu Reeves dan Carrie-Anne Moss, kembali ke dunia dua realiti - satu, kehidupan seharian; lagi satu, apa yang ada di sebaliknya.
Bintang kegemaran anda kembali bersama watak baharu, lagu-lagu dan persembahan memukau dalam Sing 2 serta komedi menarik tentang kuasa muzik.
Siaran di sebalik tabir kemunculan semula Teater Awam "Shakespeare in the Park" selepas penutupannya akibat pandemik global.

Matt, seorang CEO yang bijak dalam kewangan, membeli syarikat penerbangan serantau milik keluarga Jenny. Inisiatif penjimatan kos Matt mengancam Krismas apabila dia membatalkan faedah amal percutian tahunan syarikat penerbangan itu untuk kanak-kanak yang kurang bernasib baik.

Kisah luar biasa Nadia Nadim, bekas pelarian Afghanistan yang menjadi pemain bintang untuk Saint-Germain Paris, dan inspirasi kepada pelarian di seluruh dunia yang terpaksa meninggalkan tanah air mereka.
Pembongkaran budaya rasuah antara anggota polis Baltimore selepas kes kematian detektif Sean Suiter yang ditembak pada tahun 2017 yang masih belum selesai.

The Forever Prisoner mengisahkan tentang Abu Zubaydah, tahanan bernilai tinggi bagi program Teknik Soal Siasat yang Dipertingkatkan CIA (EIT) – juga dikenal pasti sebagai seksaan oleh orang luar agensi.
Penghormatan yang penuh inspirasi untuk pelakon dan pembuat filem Adrienne Shelly, meraikan kehidupan dan kerjanya sambil mengupas tragedi kematiannya.
Perjalanan 36 tahun ke dalam hidup tiga kawan yang terlibat dengan penagihan dadah dan jenayah di Newark, New Jersey.

Percutian ini, Liddles gembira kerana pelbagai perkara! Jacquie Liddle (Kelly Rowland) dan suaminya Tyler (Thomas Cadrot) sedang bersiap sedia untuk kelahiran bayi pertama mereka. Sementara itu, kakak Jacquie, Treena (Latonya Williams) dan suaminya Julian (Jaime M. Callica) sedang memikirkan untuk mengambil bayi angkat, dan hubungan Kiera (Bresha Webb), kakak yang bersemangat dan bergaya, dengan Chris (Nathan Witte) semakin hangat.
