info.plot: Tiga remaja menjadi kambing hitam apabila pihak polis gagal menemukan pembunuh sebenar bagi kes pembunuhan tiga orang kanak-kanak berusia lapan tahun. Filem ini merekodkan pelbagai saat-saat intim dan terbuka dalam kes ini selama setahun, dan membangkitkan beberapa persoalan mengenai individualisme, anggapan tidak bersalah, dan peranan media dalam mempengaruhi pandangan umum.
Ejen rahsia Ethan Hunt mengejar masa untuk mencari pengkhianat yang mengancam untuk menjejaskan operasi CIA. Dibintangi oleh Tom Cruise.

Pada Mei 1999, Johnny Carson, hos rancangan temu bual lewat malam terhebat memeranjatkan dunia televisyen apabila beliau mengumumkan persaraannya dalam masa setahun.  Pihak TV berebut mencari pengganti hos rancangan "The Tonight Show", iaitu program TV paling berjaya dalam sejarah yang menawan setiap rangkaian, media Amerika dan orang ramai selama lebih dua tahun.

Inilah kisah Benny Agrelo, seorang pesakit berusia 15 tahun yang sakit tenat berjuang untuk menjalani sisa hidupnya dengan caranya sendiri. Benny memutuskan untuk berhenti mengambil ubat-ubatan yang membantu badannya menerima hati yang dipindahkan kerana ia menghasilkan sejumlah kesan sampingan yang menyakitkan. Selepas meyakinkan ibunya untuk membiarkan dia menjalani bulan-bulan terakhirnya "tanpa kesakitan," Benny telah diambil dari keluarganya dengan perintah mahkamah - dan terpaksa pergi ke mahkamah untuk memerangi hak untuk menentukan nasibnya sendiri.
Seorang ibu bertindak sendiri apabila perogol bersiri yang merogol anak perempuannya dibebaskan kerana masalah teknikal undang-undang.

“Fighting 99th” adalah skuadron pertama Angkatan Tentera Udara Amerika-Afrika bertempur dengan juruterbang pesawat pejuang dalam Perang Dunia Kedua. Ketika mula berlatih, tidak ramai yang mahukan mereka dalam angkatan tentera. Mereka perlu buktikan mereka lebih kuat, kental, bijak dan mahir mengemudi pesawat berbanding juruterbang berkulit putih…. dan mereka berjaya!
Persembahan lawak tunggal istimewa 30 minit bersama Dana Gould, pelawak utama dalam edisi "One-Night Stand" HBO.
Persembahan lawak tunggal istimewa 30 minit bersama Steve Harvey.

Berlatarkan tahun 1999, Parker Barnes, bekas polis yang mempunyai kisah silam yang amat tragik dan sama kelam dengan masa depannya, dipenjara secara tidak adil dan kini diberi peluang terakhir untuk bebas. Dia perlu membunuh pembunuh yang dijana komputer kejam yang melarikan diri dari ruang siber dan memasuki dunia sebenar. Perburuan tergesa-gesa ini yang pastinya memecah sempadan antara realiti virtual dan jalan di Los Angeles!
Alicia Silvertone sebagai watak Cher, percaya dengan “buat perkara baik untuk orang lain” tapi apabila keadaan itu melibatkan soal hati terutamanya diri sendiri, dia tiada pengalaman.
Batman berdepan dengan Two-Face and the Riddler, menampilkan Val Kilmer, Chris O'Donnell, Nicole Kidman, Tommy Lee Jones dan Jim Carrey.

Filem yang meletup, pemenang tiga Anugerah Emmy dan dua Anugerah Golden Globe, mendedahkan kisah sebenar salah satu perbicaraan yang paling mahal dan panjang dalam sejarah Amerika Syarikat. McMartins adalah sebuah keluarga yang berdedikasi untuk menjaga kanak-kanak. Apabila seorang ibu menuduh mereka mendera kanak-kanak di sekolah pra, beratus-ratus ibu bapa yang risau datang ke depan dengan dakwaan yang bukan-bukan terhadap keluarga itu, termasuk ritual syaitan, pornografi kanak-kanak dan juga rogol. Memakan belanja sebanyak 15 juta dolar dan diheret selama 7 tahun, perbicaraan itu tamat tanpa seorang disabitkan bersalah, tetapi memusnahkan keseluruhan kehidupan ahli keluarga itu.

Dia kehilangan abang, ayah, ibu dan sahabatnya sewaktu Holocaust. Kemudian, apabila dia hampir mengalah kepada kebinasaan tiga bulan yang dikenali sebagai "perarakan kematian", Gerda Weissmann dibebaskan daripada mimpi ngeri selama enam tahun.

Sebuah filem biografi HBO berkenaan Mike Tyson yang terkenal. Bakatnya membawanya dari zaman kanak-kanak yang penuh kemiskinan di jalan-jalan Brooklyn kepada kemasyhuran dan tuah yang tak dijangka sebagai juara heawyweight termuda dalam sejarah tinju. Mike Tyson berada di puncak dunia sehinggalah nasihat yang tak baik serta impian jahatnya sendiri yang mengubah impiannya menjadi mimpi ngeri Amerika.

Empat orang askar lelaki Amerika Syarikat merisikon kerjaya dan hidup mereka untuk bangkit demi kepercayaan mereka, dalam drama yang membangkitkan semangat berdasarkan kisah benar. Pada tahun 1935, Jeneral Douglas MacArthur melihat peningkatan ancaman terhadap Jerman dan, berazam untuk memodenkan askar, mengarahkan unit Pasukan Kuda untuk menghapuskan 500 ekor kuda mereka yang terakhir dan bubar. Namun begitu, sekumpulan tentera, diketuai oleh veteran beruban putih Sarjan John Libbey (Johnson, Goodbye Lover, Tin Cup), nekad untuk menyelamatkan haiwan itu, dan mereka meluru merentasi dataran untuk kebebasan---bersama unit kereta kebal tentera memburu dengan hebat.

Apa yang terjadi apabila seorang penjenayah yang suka menumpahkan darah dan menyebabkan jumlah kematian yang tinggi, menghendap jalan Soviet dan mengambil nyawa petualang muda yang tidak bersalah? Penyiasatan yang lambat dan birokrasi terencat itu sendiri ialah pembunuh. Ahli patologi forensik Rusia, Burakov tidak mahukan apa-apa selain mahu kes ini diselesaikan. Selepas menjejak pembunuh bersiri itu selama bertahun-tahun, usaha memburu memberi kesan kepada dirinya. Satu-satunya sokongan datang daripada ketuanya, Fetisov. Namun masa mencemburui Burakov dan setiap petualang muda di luar sana, kerana jika pita pelekat tidak boleh membunuh mereka, pita merah boleh membunuh.

name: 5 American Handguns - 5 American Kids: America Undercover

info.plot: Apabila kanak-kanak memegang pistol tangan berisi peluru, seseorang biasanya mati. Tahun lepas, 24,000 warga Amerika terkorban akibat senjata…dan 3,600 daripadanya ialah kanak-kanak. Dokumentari yang amat membimbangkan ini menceritakan kisah lima pucuk pistol yang mengorbankan lima kanak-kanak-dan bagaimana kematian mereka mungkin dapat dielak.

Di Hollywood pada 1950-an, magik dibenarkan dan semua orang menggunakannya. Setiap orang, ya, melainkan Detektif Phillip Lovercraft. Namun kini dia menyiasat kes melibatkan penerbit yang dibunuh, isteri cantik yang juga bintang filem dan senator yang gilakan perhatian. Ahli politik itu menguruskan platform anti-magik dan merancang untuk menghantarnya ke Rumah Putih dengan membakar ahli sihir pada pancang. Ahli sihir itu adalah salah seorang kawan baik Lovercraft. Dapatkah Lovercraft menyelamatkan rakannya tanpa dia sendiri menggunakan silap mata?

Presiden A.S. hampir digulingkan dalam rampasan kuasa tentera, dan seorang kolonel Pentagon hanya mempunyai satu minggu untuk menghentikannya. Namun sebelum itu, dia perlu membuktikan bahawa plot untuk merancang rampasan kuasa wujud. Forest Whitaker membintangi drama suspens seram ini sebagai pegawai yang setia, mengejar masa untuk mendapatkan bukti utama yang diperlukan untuk menghalang jeneral yang dahagakan kuasa daripada merampas kerajaan. Jason Robards adalah dalang kejam di sebalik plot maut itu.
Pelawak yang gila-gila, Eddie Griffin membuat persembahan tanpa tapisan dalam persembahan tunggal istimewa selama 30 minit ini.
Pelawak homoseksual yang lantang, pelawak utama di kelab komedi di seluruh negara, sentiasa memastikan penontonnya geli hati dengan rutin jenakanya yang inovatif.

Apa yang membawa seorang peLajar pintar kepada kehidupan jenayah? Bagi Eddie Matos yang tinggal di kawasan berpendapatan rendah, menjual dadah adalah tiket kepada wang, populariti dan kuasa. Ia juga tiket kepada bencana. Drama berdasarkan fakta ini menceritakan kisah Eddie, menunjukkan bagaimana tekanan sosial membuat Eddie memilih kehidupan di jalan yang salah dari segi undang-undang, menunjukkan akibat tragik disebabkan pilihan itu.

name: Lock Up: The Prisoners Of Rikers Island

info.plot: Jika anda ditangkap di New York City dan tidak boleh diikat jamin, anda akan dihantar ke Rikers Island - sebuah fasiliti raksasa yang menampung seramai 17,000 lelaki dan wanita menunggu untuk dibicarakan. Wartawan televisyen terkenal Jon Alpert menghabiskann masa selama 10 bulan untuk melakukan penggambaran di sana, disertai grafik dan gambaran tidak berkerdip kehidupan di dalam kompleks penjara terbesar Amerika, termasuk pandangan yang mengharukan pada wajah banduan-banduan disebalik statistik.

Sepuluh lelaki berdepan sungai yang ganas dan berbahaya. Bagi Alan Alda seorang ketua di agensi pengiklanan, aktiviti berakit hujung minggu ini sepatutnya menguji kelelakian anak-anak buahnya dan sekali gus membuktikan kewibawaannya sebagai seorang ketua.Tetapi sejauh mana anda akan pergi demi kuasa dan pangkat apabila nyawa orang lain dalam bahaya? Peter Gallagher membintangi drama mengujakan ini sebagai seorang eksekutif junior yang mula ragu-ragu dengan komitmennya terhadap agensi tersebut. Robert Loggia membawa watak bekas rakan sekerja Alda.

name: Confronting Brandon: The Intervention Of An Addict

info.plot: Apa yang anda lakukan apabila pengambilan dadah dan alkohol menyebabkan rakan menjadi tidak terkawal? Dalam drama berdasarkan fakta sebenar, pelajar sekolah menengah tinggi, Brandon Clifton enggan mengakui bahawa dia mempunyai masalah - sehingga rakan-rakan dan kaunselor yang mengambil berat menganjurkan "campur tangan"; konfrontasi langsung yang memaksa Clifton berdepan kebenaran tentang dirinya.

Bunuh diri remaja adalah subjek drama menyentuh hati ini yang berdasarkan kisah benar. Robert Bierer menceritakan semula kejadian yang membawa kepada pembunuhan diri rakan baiknya, Dale King, dan mengimbau semula tanda amaran yang tiada siapa peduli sehingga ia sudah terlambat. Perkara sensitif. Budi bicara ibu bapa diperlukan.

Filmed in front of a live audience in Brooklyn, Martin Lawrence turns his comedy spotlight on (among other things) racism, poverty, Jeffrey Dahmer, looters, sex and the differences between men and women.

name: Lifestories 10: Families In Crisis: A Child Betrayed: The Calvin Mire Story

info.plot: Apa yang patut dilakukan oleh kanak-kanak lelaki berusia 11 tahun apabila salah seorang individu paling dipercayai - paderi Katolik - melakukan penderaan seksual? Drama berdasarkan fakta ini mengikuti kisah Calvin Mire, pembantu paderi lurus yang bercita-cita mahu berkhidmat kepada Tuhan bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila dia dicabul oleh kariah paderi. Kandungan sensitif. Budi bicara ibu bapa diperlukan.

Lakonan semula yang sukar tentang rusuhan penjara Attica 1971 ini padat dengan implikasi politik dan sosial. Tanpa dijangka, tiada satu pun watak dalam filem -- banduan, pengawal dan perantara berprofil tinggi, disampaikan dengan anggapan lelaki baik atau lelaki jahat oleh penulis skrip Ron Hutchinson. Sesiapa yang cukup dewasa untuk menyaksikan liputan rusuhan asal di TV secara langsung, walau bagaimanapun, dapat membezakan siapa yang benar-benar bertanggungjawab atas hasil tragik itu. Sementara filem-TV 1971 "Attica" disampaikan daripada pandangan wartawan, drama ini disampaikan menerusi pandangan idealistik pengawal penjara muda bernama Michael Smith.
Persembahan lawak tunggal bersama salah seorang daripada dua bintang rancangan TV popular di HBO, Mr. Show With Bob and David.
Bergelak ketawa selama 30 minit bersama pelawak Korea-Amerika, Margaret Cho.
Pelawak ini membuat persembahan tanpa tapisan di hadapan penonton studio.

Memperkenalkan wanita yang besar, cantik dan amat kelakar yang mendakwa nama sebenarnya ialah 'Absolutely Fantastic'! Mengejutkan dan mempunyai pendapat sendiri, Simply hanya bertumpu kepada topik seperti pendakwah yang menyanyi, saiz badannya, dan cara terbaik untuk melakukan hubungan seks selamat ("kunci pintu *#@%$ !").

name: Autopsy: Confessions Of A Medical Examiner

info.plot: Bolehkah orang yang meninggal bersuara? Ya... tetapi hanya kepada mereka yang tahu mendengar. Dalam dokumentari mengagumkan ini, Dr. Michael Baden, salah seorang ahli patologi forensik paling terkenal dalam negara, mendedahkan kisah di sebalik kes yang tidak normal atau kematian mencurigakan yang dia bantu menyelesaikannya. Dalam lebih 20,000 autopsi selama lebih 32 tahun, Dr. Baden menemui banyak rahsia kematian dan membawa pembunuh ke muka pengadilan, melayakkannya mendapat nama gelaran,"detektif kematian."

When the city’s most feared gangsters are systematically eliminated, the Caped Crusader is blames. But prowling the Gotham night is a shadowy new villain, the Phantasm, a sinister figure with some link to Batman’s past. Can the Dark Knight elude the police, capture the Phantasm and clear his name.

Bagi sesetengah orang, Perang Saudara tidak pernah berakhir. Graff(Mickey Rourke) antaranya. Bersama dengan rakan seperjuangan bekas askar Confederate, dia bertindak merompak bank-bank Yankee. Graff seorang ketua yang tegas dan berdisiplin hinggakan pengikutnya akur pada arahannya tanpa banyak soal hinggalah apabila satu rompakan bank bertukar menjadi pembunuhan besar-besaran.  Graff terselamat akibat pembelotan orangnya sendiri dan kembali melunas dendam.

Pada musim panas 1981, wabak jangkitan yang jarang ditemui dilaporkan. Penyakit bermisteri yang baru ini, seperti hanya menjangkiti lelaki homoseksual sahaja dan tidak menjadi ancaman kepada orang lain. Pihak media yang selalunya menggembar-gemburkan berita seperti ini kini melihatnya sudah tidak begitu penting. Filem HBO Original ini membabadkan tempoh awal ketika wabak AIDS mula merebak dan sekumpulan kecil individu yang berusaha untuk mengubah sikap tidak peduli, kejahilan dan politik untuk melawan wabak maut yang akan mengubah dunia.
This feature film features the popular cartoon of cat and mouse game of Tom and Jerry. In the story, the two are trying to help an orphan girl who is being tortured by her greedy guardian.
Filem arahan Steven Spielberg mengisahkan sekumpulan saintis di pulau yang menyaksikan dinosaur sebenar di taman dan akhirnya semuanya bertukar menjadi tragedi.

Tidak lama lagi, Amerika akan diserang satu wabak yang boleh mengancam nyawa…satu-satunya tindakan pihak kerajaan adalah dengan mengkuarantin mangsa yang dijangkiti. Sekumpulan pemberontak mencabar tindakan ini…dan sepasang kekasih muda cuba mencari harapan di dunia yang sudah tiada lagi harapan. Cuba Gooding Jr. (Boyz N the Hood) dan Moira Kelly (With Honors) membintangi drama penuh aksi ini. Turut berlakon, Omar Epps (Juice) dan Martha Plimpton (Parenthood).

name: Skinheads Usa: Soldiers Of The Race War

info.plot: Hitler adalah wira mereka, White Power adalah slogan mereka. Mereka adalah ahli kepada Aryan National Front, dan anda akan berjumpa dengan mereka dalam filem yang mengejutkan ini. Buat kali pertama, HBO membawa anda ke dalam organisasi Skinhead neo-Nazi untuk melihat cara dan mentaliti pergerakan White Power di Amerika.

name: Dead Drunk: The Kevin Tunell Story

info.plot: Setiap tahun, lebih 200,000 anak muda terlibat dalam kemalangan kereta melibatkan alkohol, dengan sekurang-kurang 5,000 daripadanya maut akibat perkara itu. Drama mengganggu perasaan ini menceritakan kisah sebenar Kevin Tunell, yang terlibat dalam kemalangan memandu mabuk semasa dia berusia 17 tahun dan menyebabkan kematian gadis berusia 18 tahun; dan meninggalkannya dengan penderitaan, ingatan dan penyesalan seumur hidup. Kandungan sensitif. Budi bicara ibu bapa disyorkan.

name: No Visible Bruises: The Katie Koestner Story

info.plot: Seorang pelajar yang pemalu dari sekolah campuran memutuskan untuk mendakwa teman sekelas yang didakwa merogolnya pada janji temu pertama mereka -- meskipun kekurangan bukti keterangan mengikut keadaan, dan kenaifan dirinya sendiri yang menganggap lelaki itu boleh dipercayai pada awalnya.

Mereka "sahabat sejati" sebenar: "Joe Dogs" Iannuzzi, Tommy DelGiorno, "Big Dom" Lofaro. Buat kali pertama dalam televisyen, pembelot mafia menceritakan sendiri kisah peribadi kehidupan dalam geng. Dalam dokumentari mengejutkan ini, lima pemberi maklumat yang berkedudukan tinggi meceritakan kisah pembunuhan, kejam, tamak dan megah diri--dan punca mereka memecahkan kod Sicilian yang dibanggakan.

Kisah keberanian, kanak-kanak lelaki Brooklyn berusia 11 tahun yang bangkit untuk menceritakan kepada dunia bahawa dia memiliki virus AIDS --dan orang yang berdiri bersama-samanya dalam berdepan prasangka masyarakat. Bahan sensitif. Budi bicara ibu bapa disyorkan.

name: Gunplay: The Last Day In The Life Of Brian Darling

info.plot: Ia hari biasa buat Brian yang berusia 10 tahun: sekolah, permainan dan menonton TV… sehinggalah dia dan rakannya bermain dengan pistol sebenar. Drama HBO Original ini menceritakan kisah tragik dan benar seorang budak lelaki yang tidak sengaja maut akibat senjata berpeluru. John Darling, bapa budak itu, memperkenalkan filem ini, dan pada bahagian kesimpulan memberikan lima petua keselamatan senjata untuk kanak-kanak dan orang dewasa, berharap dapat mengurangkan statistik menggerunkan kanak-kanak yang terbunuh dalam kemalangan pistol. Amaran penonton: program ini perlu ditonton oleh kanak-kanak dengan bimbingan orang dewasa.

name: Public Law 106: The Becky Bell Story

info.plot: Apabila remaja dari Indiana, Becky Bell hamil, dia berasa takut untuk memberitahu ibu bapanya. Undang-undang kebenaran ibu bapa di negerinya tidak membenarkannya untuk melakukan pengguguran secara sah. Terdesak, dan merasakan dia tiada tempat untuk dituju, dia memilih untuk menggugurkan kandungannya secara haram - dengan akibat yang tragik.

name: The Secret Life Of Mary-Margaret: Portrait Of A Bulimic

info.plot: Bahagian kedua siri HBO LifeStories: Families in Crisis, The Secret Life of Mary-Margaret adalah dramatisasi kejadian yang membawa remaja biasa menjadi mangsa bulimia -- kecelaruan makan biasa namun sering disalah erti. Dibintangi Calista Flockhart sebagai watak utama, filem ini berakhir dengan kemunculan Mary-Margaret sebenar, yang memberitahu penyebab kecelaruan makan dan menggalakkan orang dengan simptom bulimia untuk meminta bantuan.
Penguin, seorang penjenayah cacat, mengancam bandar Gotham dan bandar itu berdoa untuk kepulangan Batman.
Riggs dan Murtaugh, yang dilakonkan oleh Mel Gibson dan Danny Glover, menjadikan Los Angeles riuh-rendah sekali lagi dalam siri ketiga filem aksi terbaik ini!

Pandangan memprovokasi dan tegang tentang sisi manusia berkaitan isu moral dan politik paling sensitif sekarang. Dokumentari yang memenangi Emmy ini menyertakan bahan visual klinik pengguguran sebenar, begitu juga testimoni dari tiga generasi wanita Amerika yang kehidupan mereka berubah selama-lamanya kerana pengguguran.

Graham Greene (Dances With Wolves) membintangi sebagai Ishi, orang asli India liar terakhir di Amerika. Jon Voight memegang watak ahli antropologi yang membawa Ishi ke San Francisco untuk mengkajinya dan mengajarnya cara "bertamadun" dan mendapati terdapat banyak perkara yang dia perlu belajar daripada lelaki "yang tidak bertamadun" berbanding yang dia bayangkan.

Apa yang berlaku apabila seorang jutawan menderma kekayaannya dan bermula semula? Jack Lemmon berharap dapat memberi pengajaran kepada anak dan isterinya yang manja... dan mungkin menghidupkan semula asmara dalam perkahwinan mereka. Namun, ia tidak semestinya berjalan seperti yang dirancang dan sebelum keluarga itu mengecapi kebahagiaan bersama semula, terdapat beberapa kejutan yang menanti mereka! Talia Shire dan Jonathan Silverman digandingkan dalam komedi yang mengharukan ini.

name: The Iceman Tapes: Conversations With A Killer

info.plot: Richard Kuklinski suami yang setia, bapa penyayang dan pembunuh tidak berhati perut. Anda akan bertemu dengannya dalam dokumentari hebat yang menampilkan salah satu temu bual paling jelas dan mengganggu yang pernah dirakam--dirakam di belakang dinding penjara tempat Kuklinski menjalani dua hukuman penjara seumur hidup atas beberapa pembunuhan.

Dalam filem HBO Original mendebarkan ini yang menambah keterujaan detektif dengan ancaman kuasa ghaib, detektif 40-an H. Philli Lovercraft (Fred Ward) menyelesaikan kes terakhirnya. Diupah oleh klien kaya untuk menentukan lokasi buku yang dicuri tentang ilmu sihir hanya dalam 48 jam, tugas penyamaran Lovercraft mendedahkan hakikat mengejutkan: buku itu boleh memusnahkan dunia jika ia jatuh ke tangan yang salah. Dapatkah dia melawan kuasa kejam dalam mencari kuasa paling kuat--dan perempuan penggoda berbahaya--dan terselamat untuk menceritakan tentangnya?

name: Without Warning: The James Brady Story

info.plot: Cubaan membunuh Presiden Ronald Reagen pada tahun 1981 mengakibatkan setiausaha akhbarnya, Jim Brady cedera parah. Kini, buat kali pertama, adalah kisah dalaman dramatik kejayaan 10 tahun perjuangan keluarga Brady dengan tragedi, disampaikan penuh menyentuh hati oleh Beau Bridges sebagai "Bear" Brady dan Joan Allen sebagai isterinya yang berani, Sarah.
This celebration of a half century of laughs brought to audiences around the world by the beloved cat and mouse includes highlights of the duo's best cartoons, which have won seven Academy Awards.

Suara tegap dan garau Blake Clark yang menghasilkan jenaka "di luar gerak hati untuk penjagaan" menyerlahkan gaya unik jenaka memerhatinya kepada komedi istimewa ini. Dirakam di Panggung Ohio di Cleveland, sorotan episod istimewa ini bertumpu kepada komedi lebih santai, merangkumi segalanya daripada burger keju yang rumit, budaya Selatan dan gangguan kerajaan, bahaya tersembunyi memandu di lebuh raya, tekanan dalam kehidupan harian dan rahsia sebenar di sebalik Victoria's Secret.

Seorang paderi Katolik menyimpan rahsia memeranjatkan. Namun mengapa orang atasannya bersungguh-sungguh mahu melindunginya? Dalam drama yang tegang ini, Keith Carradine dan Blythe Danner memainkan watak ibu bapa yang bangga dan warak kepada pembantu paderi berusia lapan tahun yang diliwat oleh paderi. Pasangan ini terkejut apabila hierarki gereja cuba membayar mereka agar berdiam diri. Namun dengan bantuan daripada peguam Cajun (Jack Warden), mereka menemui rahsia yang membawa mereka untuk berjuang mendapatkan keadilan--walau apa-apa juga caranya. Dengan David Strathairn.

Bolehkah seorang guru yang agak sopan santun berdepan dengan penjenayah kejam, El Diablo? Apa saja mungkin berlaku dalam filem komedi ini. Seorang guru muda di Texas, Billy Ray (Edwards, The Forgotten, ER) berjanji akan menyelamatkan seorang kanak-kanak yang diculik oleh El Diablo. Orang baru ini bersepakat dengan penembak berpengalaman, Van Leek (Gossett Jr, pemenang Anugerah Academy untuk An Officer And A Gentleman). Mampukah mereka selamatkan kanak-kanak itu, diri mereka dan peroleh keuntungan dalam perjalanan?
Tom Cruise dan Nicole Kidman membintangi drama mengenai pemandu kereta lumba yang perlu menghadapi kehidupan di dalam dan di luar trek selepas kecederaan yang serius.
Seorang polis San Francisco, suspek utama dalam kejadian tembakan, terpaksa bekerjasama semula dengan bekas bandan untuk membersihkan namanya. Dibintangi Eddie Murphy.

Pada Zaman Keemasan Emas Hollywood, dua lelaki ini memiliki segala-galanya: seorang ialah penulis skrip yang terkenal, seorang lagi ialah idola filem Matinee. Namun apabila pemburu sihir McCarthyism masuk ke dalam Tinseltown, seorang lelaki melarikan diri dari negara dan seorang lagi membunuh diri. Ron Silver membintangi drama bergaya ini tentang seorang lelaki yang tekad untuk melawan ketidakadilan. Hart Bochner melakonkan watak rakan bintang filem yang terseksa dan Daniel J. Travanti ialah lelaki yang mengkhianati mereka dalam "muslihat politik yang mengujakan dan sofistikated".

Kyra Sedgwick (Twelfth Night), Stanley Tucci (A Midsummer Night?s Dream), Robbie Coltrane (The World Is Not Enough) Robin Tunney (End of Days) dan John Ritter membintangi filem seram tentang pembunuh upahan profesional wanita yang disasarkan oleh organisasinya sendiri. Claire (Sedgwick) ialah pembunuh upahan berjaya yang menyerahkan segalanya kepada majikannya (Coltrane). Namun apabila majikan itu memberi tugas tahap rendah kepada Claire supaya mencari teman wanitanya yang hilang, Kitty, Claire tahu dia terlalu gembira. Tambah memburukkan keadaan, teman wanita (Tunney) melakukan pembunuhan semasa Claire dalam tahanan. Terpaksa lari dari sindiket sendiri, Claire kemudiannya mendapati Kitty perempuan penggoda dan perlu berhati-hati dengannya. Tucci dalam keadaan baik membawa watak Nick Claire, kekasih yang sakit tenat dan rakan pembunuh upahan.

name: Earth To Kids: A Guide To Products For A Healthy Planet

info.plot: Adakah anda tahu tiga R untuk menjadikan Bumi tempat yang lebih baik untuk didiami? Anda akan mempelajari cara untuk mengurangkan, menggunakan semula dan mengitar semula sampah dalam program menarik dan memberi maklumat ini yang diterbitkan oleh HBO dan Televisyen Laporan Pengguna. Kanak-kanak boleh membawa perubahan dan menjadi pengguna yang bijak, kerana skit yang menarik, pertunjukan kreatif dan rancangan segmen animasi yang meriah. Ketahui jika anda patut membeli ubat gigi dalam pam atau tiub, barang bungkusan dalam plastik atau kaca dan lebih lagi. Selain itu, saksikan beberapa petua menghiburkan dan mudah tentang cara menjadikan planet kita tempat yang lebih sihat.
Pasangan polis dinamik, Mel Gibson dan Danny Glover, kembali untuk aksi yang lebih menarik dalam filem kedua pengembaraan penuh aksi ini!
Bruce Wayne, trauma dengan kematian ibu bapanya, mendedikasikan kehidupannya untuk memerangi jenayah sebagai Batman.

Semuanya bermula di lorong gelap dengan kematian ngeri dua wartawan, seorang "pengemis" dan tiga Mafia. Atau betulkah? Bagi makhluk misteri Spawn, perjalanannya bermula lima tahun sebelum ini, semasa dia CIA operasi bernama Al Simmons, dan dipenjarakan hingga mati di bawah keadaan misteri. Terdesak untuk berjumpa isteri kesayangannya, Wanda, sekali lagi, Al buat satu perjanjian dengan syaitan, Malebolgia, dan setuju untuk menukar jiwanya untuk kembali ke bumi buat kali terakhir. Hanya selepas perjanjian itu, barulah Al menyedari dia akan dihantar lima tahun ke hadapan, tanpa kenangannya, dan kuasa pelik yang hebat. Semasa lima tahun itu, Wanda berkahwin semula dengan kawan baik Al, Terry, dan akhirnya mendapat anak yang dimahukan dengan Al. Mengetahui hal lalu dalam daripada "ejen" Badut neraka, Spawn bergelut menentang sifat gelap dan ganasnya dan dalam perjalanan temui diri sendiri yang ganas dan tidak menyenangkan.
Beberapa polis yang berbeza latar belakangnya terperangkap antara satu sama lain sebagai rakan sepasukan dan ditugaskan untuk menyiasat kes bunuh diri dan sebuah kumpulan jenayah antarabangsa.

Sekali dalam ribuan generasi, seorang anak dengan kekuatan gaib lahir -- untuk membawa kebaikan ke dunia. Ketika kekuatan iblis menculik sang anak sempurna ini, pencarian dirinya menjadi hal terpenting di Bumi. Seorang pekerja sosial LA terkesima ketika mengetahui bahwa ia adalah 'orang yang terpilih' untuk menyelamatkan anak tersebut dari iblis. Ketika itulah, ia terlibat dalam suatu perjalanan fantastik yang membawanya dari California ke Tiongkok, dan bahkan ke Neraka.
Seorang pelajar sekolah senior ponteng sekolah untuk melepak dengan kawan-kawannya dalam filem komedi John Hughes klasik ini.

Inilah kisah sebenar penuh emosi keberanian dan daya ketahanan Terry Fox (Fryer). Walaupun kehilangan kaki kepada kanser, Canadian Fox mula mengekalkan semangatnya dan dengan bantuan anggota palsu, dia memutuskan untuk berlari di seluruh negara dalam perkara yang dikenali sebagai Maraton Harapan, untuk mencari duit bagi kajian perubatan. Dia berjoging sebanyak 3,000 batu di seluruh Kanada sebelum mati daripada kepenatan.
Seorang yang banduan keluar masuk penjara dan seorang detektif bekerjasama untuk  menangkap pasangan banduan itu yang telah melarikan diri.

A little boy tries to help a stranded extraterrestrial return to its outer-space home. When 10-year-old Elliott discovers the creature hiding behind his house, it launches a heartfelt friendship – and a mission to return ET to his home before devious government workers place him in captivity.

Filem ini memaparkan kehidupan di Bronx Selatan yang terkenal, New York, dan pusatnya ialah "Fort Apache", tempat yang dianggap oleh pegawai polis sebagai balai polis mereka tapi ia sebenarnya kota kara di negara musuh. Konflik dalam kalangan pegawai polis adalah perkara biasa, yang menyebabkan kematian dua pegawai polis baru. Namun, di kawasan bergolak begitu, semua orang mendapati sukar untuk mendapatkan penyelesaian bagi kes ini.
Di sebuah hotel peranginan bersalji, kengerian dari masa lalu menghantui fikiran seorang lelaki yang bercuti bersama keluarganya.

name: On Location: An Evening With Robert Klein

info.plot: Inilah Classic Klein dalam acara komedi tunggal istimewa bersejarah pada 1975-- yang pertama seumpamanya ditayang di HBO - dirakam secara langsung di Kolej Haverford di New Jersey. Memakai baju panas berwarna-warni, pelawak legenda ini memberikan pandangan terhadap perniagaan TV kabel yang yang baru sebelum ini, datang ke kolej di New York, dan banyak lagi--selain rutinnya yang menggelikan hati "Saya tak boleh berhenti gerakkan kaki!"

On a certain island in the Pacific, an invincible human-smuggling organization kidnaps and defrauds Chinese people. In order to rescue his kidnapped adopted daughter, the usually taciturn Chen does not hesitate to reveal the secret past he has concealed for twenty years, and joins hands with the local young policeman Can to fight against a huge criminal organization, engaging in a life-or-death battle with evil forces.

This film is made based on the real stories that took place at an abadoned house in Johor called Villa Nabila. Director Syafiq Yusof chooses to present the film in a documentary style. The film starts off with a disappearance of a teenager at the house. Syafiq interviews a few individuals who claim to have experience the supernatural at the house and turns the interview into a film.

name: 猪猪侠大电影·星际行动

info.plot: Izzah a simple kampong teacher is sold to a brothel by her uncle on the pretext that they need money for her Aunt's surgery. Her first customer is Rich playboy Hariz whom she begs to marry her and take her out of the rat hole. He marries her, brings her home, the only good deed he has done in a long time. Unknowingly he falls in love with her, and wants to break his engagement to childhood family friend Mila, but due to family pressure has to marry Mila. Thus begins the triangle of a saga which entangles three lives into a myriad of emotions.

Based on the all time best-selling novel, Kasyah (Farid Kamil) is a troublemaker in high school but things change when he meets Ayu (Lisa Surihani). However, Kasyah is force to part with Ayu when he has to go for a research project. Ayu then meets her ex-lover Azmi (Que Haidar) who is an abuser.

After the death of Ayu, Kasyah raised their daughter Athirah all by himself. Katherina met with Kasyah again even though she was heartbroken. When their love has gone stronger they have to go through many challenges in order to make the relationship works. Will their love survive? Watch this epic love story and find out...

Putri is determined to win back her sports-mad ex-boyfriend, Eddy by turning into a futsal heroine herself. Facing prejudice and ridicule, and discovering, through her motley futsal team, the many difficulties faced by women in sports, Putri gradually finds within herself the strength and values of a true winner, on and off the pitch.

Gol & Gincu Vol. 2 tells a story about Zakiah (Zak) and Zakiah (Yaya) who are two self-centered University students with the same name but very different personalities. Hauled up by the University board after a public fight that goes viral on social media, the girls face disciplinary action which means hours of community work to set a good example. They volunteer at a troubled teenage girls home run by Jijie. Zak and Yaya proceed to carry out their obligatory punishment but realise its not as easy as they think. Can they set aside their mobile phones and prejudices to really be useful to Jijie and the teenage girls or will they make matters worse by being there. And what was the fight all about anyway?

Seven years after Jason, Orked is now married to a much older guy, Arif. Everything seems ideal in their marriage at first glance. One fateful morning, Orked is awakened by a distressing phone call from Mak Inom with news that Pak Atan has become catatonic due to diabetic complications.After some chaos, they take Pak Atan to the hospital. There, Orked bumps into Alan, Jason’s elder brother. His father, Pa has also been hospitalized. As the film develops, we witness the friendship between Alan and Orked flourish, to Arif’s apprehension. Perhaps because for Orked, Alan is a link to her first love.
Bawang Putih lives with her stepmother and stepsister and is abused every day. Putih escapes and encounters the handsome Prince in the forest of Inderaloka.
Bawang Putih lives with her stepmother and stepsister and is abused every day. Putih escapes and encounters the handsome Prince in the forest of Inderaloka.
Bawang Putih lives with her stepmother and stepsister and is abused every day. Putih escapes and encounters the handsome Prince in the forest of Inderaloka.
Bawang Putih lives with her stepmother and stepsister and is abused every day. Putih escapes and encounters the handsome Prince in the forest of Inderaloka.
Bawang Putih lives with her stepmother and stepsister and is abused every day. Putih escapes and encounters the handsome Prince in the forest of Inderaloka.
A group of artists’ lives becomes unwittingly entangled as their obsessions and insecurities manifest monsters, demons and death.

The True story of how charismatic con man Jason Derek Brown bankrolls his extravagant lifestyle through a series of scams. On Brown’s trail: Lance Leising, a dogged FBI special agent determined to put Brown behind bars. When Brown’s funds run low and his past catches up with him, he plots his most elaborate scheme yet, pitting himself against Leising in a deadly game of cat and mouse — and becoming the most unlikely and elusive fugitive on the FBI’s most-wanted list.

The reception for Finland's Independence Day is rudely interrupted when the presidential palace is attacked and the state leadership is taken hostage. Max Tanner of the Security Police is appointed as a negotiator in the hostage crisis, that unfolds as part of a bigger plan to undermine European security.

After a gang of violent outlaws forces a Native American woman to lead them through a treacherous forest in search of a fortune in gold, they unknowingly awaken an ancient, bloodthirsty beast that will stop at nothing to annihilate them all.

In the near future, the world is ruled by the Smart Brain Corporation, with 90% of the population being Orphnoch, and the once prominent human race is nearing extinction. Takumi Inui, Kamen Rider Faiz, was once regarded as mankind’s savior until, in an attack by Smart Brain troops, he was presumed dead. Since then, human rebel groups have staged attacks on Smart Brain’s complex in an attempt to steal the top-secret Emperor Belts, with no success. Kiba Yuji, Naoya Kaidō and Yuka Osada attempt to ease tensions between both races but their peace meeting is interrupted by Smart Brain troops and their newest warrior, Kamen Rider Psyga. Takumi, believing himself a young cobbler named Takeshi, regains his memory and becomes Kamen Rider Faiz again to settle things with Smart Brain once and for all.

name: Kamen Rider Agito Special: A New Transformation

info.plot: Shouichi encounters his old friend and caretaker Dr. Higashi Kunieda. Dr. Kunieda, a friend of Yoshihiko Misugi, took care of him while he was hospitalized with amnesia. After catching up on a year of separation Shouichi abruptly leaves to house to fight an Unknown as Agito Burning Form. Unfortunately, after the Unknown flees Shouichi loses control of himself and attacks Dr. Kunieda, who followed Shoucihi and watched him transform. Dr. Kunieda managed to calm him down but Shouichi becomes to afraid of himself and runs away.

name: Kamen Rider Ryuki Hyper Battle Video: Ryuki vs. Kamen Rider Agito

info.plot: A horde of assorted Mirror Monsters roam a warehouse, a mysterious figure resembling Agito Burning Form calling for the Kamen Riders to come fight them and die.

Shouichi encounters a teenage girl called Sayaka, who ran away from a military facility because of an attack by the Ant Lords. Sayaka has a supernatural ability to foresee the future. Risa Fukami, of the military group GA, wants to use that power to enhance the newly-made G4 System, which was based upon designs stolen from Ozawa.  Now, Agito and Gills must fight to stop the Ant Lords' attack, as G3 and G4 settle their score.
A special bond develops between plus-sized inflatable robot Baymax, and prodigy Hiro Hamada, who team up with a group of friends to form a band of high-tech heroes.

Star race car Lightning McQueen and his pal Mater head overseas to compete in the World Grand Prix race. But the road to the championship becomes rocky as Mater gets caught up in an intriguing adventure of his own: international espionage.

Despite his family’s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel's family history.
Gru and his wife Lucy must stop former '80s child star Balthazar Bratt from achieving world domination.

name: Doraemon: Nobita and the Island of Miracles – Animal Adventure

info.plot: Nobita and Doraemon use time tree Mochi and catch a big bird, which has been extinct for 500 years ago. To protect the animal, Nobita and Doraemon go to Beremon Island, overseen by a golden beetle named Herakles.

The tale of an extraordinary family, the Madrigals, who live hidden in the mountains of Colombia, in a magical house, in a vibrant town, in a wondrous, charmed place called an Encanto. The magic of the Encanto has blessed every child in the family—every child except one, Mirabel. But when she discovers that the magic surrounding the Encanto is in danger, Mirabel decides that she, the only ordinary Madrigal, might just be her exceptional family's last hope.

Nemo, an adventurous young clownfish, is unexpectedly taken from his Great Barrier Reef home to a dentist's office aquarium. It's up to his worrisome father Marlin and a friendly but forgetful fish Dory to bring Nemo home -- meeting vegetarian sharks, surfer dude turtles, hypnotic jellyfish, hungry seagulls, and more along the way.
Elsa, Anna, Kristoff and Olaf head far into the forest to learn the truth about an ancient mystery of their kingdom.

Sophie, a young milliner, is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.
Elastigirl springs into action to save the day, while Mr. Incredible faces his greatest challenge yet – taking care of the problems of his three children.

Khan Kluay is an elephant of King Naresuan the Great. Shaba Kaew, his beloved one, keeps a secret that she is pregnant. He must face three properties that belong to him - sacrifice, courage and stable love deep in his heart - to struggle through obstacles.

The story begins with three Aliens in human form preparing for a ritual to feed the Fog Mother's "siblings". The Fog Mother last came to earth during the Prehistoric Age and is the cause of the extinction of the dinosaurs. Kenji and his kid sister are in the mountains, investigating all the deaths of animals and trees there. The Fog Mother sends the three aliens, "Gorai", "Zuu", and "Agito" to kidnap Kenji's baby sister for the sacrifice.

Luca and his best friend Alberto experience an unforgettable summer on the Italian Riviera. But all the fun is threatened by a deeply-held secret: they are sea monsters from another world just below the water’s surface.
In Ancient Polynesia, when a terrible curse incurred by Maui reaches an impetuous Chieftain's daughter's island, she answers the Ocean's call to seek out the demigod to set things right.
A look at the relationship between Mike and Sulley during their days at Monsters University — when they weren't necessarily the best of friends.

name: My Little Pony: A New Generation

info.plot: Equestria's divided. But a bright-eyed hero believes Earth Ponies, Pegasi and Unicorns should be pals — and, hoof to heart, she’s determined to prove it.

Two sisters move to the country with their father in order to be closer to their hospitalized mother, and discover the surrounding trees are inhabited by Totoros, magical spirits of the forest. When the youngest runs away from home, the older sister seeks help from the spirits to find her.
In a suburban fantasy world, two teenage elf brothers embark on an extraordinary quest to discover if there is still a little magic left out there.

When Nebulous Industries announces they are recruiting Rabbids for a mission to Mars, Hibernation Rabbid doesn’t think twice. As a genius Rabbid misunderstood by his stupid peers, he has always dreamed of going to the red planet. He takes off with three other Rabbids: Disco, the lively queen of the dance-floor, Cosmo, the pilot and Mini, the adorable tiny Rabbid. Facing an interplanetary space threat, our heroes will have to learn how to overcome their differences and understand that true wisdom comes from the heart!
In a world where walking, talking, digitally connected bots have become children's best friends, an 11-year-old finds that his robot buddy doesn't quite work the same as the others do.
This movie is an alternate ending to the series, taking place after the events of episode 46. With only six Riders remaining in the Rider War, Shirō Kanzaki feels that time is running short.

This television special is an alternate telling of the Kamen Rider Ryuki story. Shinji Kido's life, working as an employee at ORE Journal, takes a sharp turn after being pulled into the Mirror World by a Mispider. Luckily, he was saved by Kamen Rider Ryuki, Koichi Sakakibara. However, Sakakibara could no longer go on due to the severity of his injuries and passed his Card Deck to Shinji, allowing him to become the next Ryuki and defeat the monster.

Doctors Kazamatsuri and Onizuka are geneticists researching cures on diseases such as AIDS and cancer by performing experiments to strengthen the human body. The test subject is Shin Kazamatsuri, motorcycle racer son of Doctor Kazamatsuri. Unknown to them, their operation is funded by a syndicate group, who plan to use this research to have the bodies of men strengthened for their own gain—they have already been experimenting in the field of cyborg soldiers, to a less-than-successful attempt. However, they did not count on Onizuka's own secret ambitions; the mad Onizuka wanted to create a new species, by fusing a grasshopper's DNA with the test subject's, in order to start a new civilization and be their god. He has tested on himself, but seems to be having greater success with Shin.

A bored and domesticated Shrek pacts with deal-maker Rumpelstiltskin to get back to feeling like a real ogre again, but when he's duped and sent to a twisted version of Far Far Away—where Rumpelstiltskin is king, ogres are hunted, and he and Fiona have never met—he sets out to restore his world and reclaim his true love.

The King of Far Far Away has died and Shrek and Fiona are to become King & Queen. However, Shrek wants to return to his cozy swamp and live in peace and quiet, so when he finds out there is another heir to the throne, they set off to bring him back to rule the kingdom.

A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.
Sewashi and Doraemon find themselves way back in time and meet Nobita. It is up to Doraemon to take care of Nobita or else he will not return to the present.

The special opens with Tachibana Tōbei taking some children to a Kamen Rider roadshow. Just as he's reminiscing about all the heroic modified humans he's lived alongside- Ichigō, Nigō, V3, Riderman, X, Amazon, Stronger and Tackle- the first seven Riders gradually show up to greet him in their human guises, unrecognised by the crowds. When it's revealed that the kaijin onstage are 'real', not actors, the Riders transform to save the crowd and Rider actors, uniting their power to defeat the Delzer Army's true leader, Great General Darkness in his hideout beneath the stadium.

The Dogma Kingdom attacks the Matagi (mountain tribe) village of Yamabiko to steal the sacred Flying Dragon Fortress and wreak havoc all over Japan. Six children from the fallen village take refuge in a nearby town, keeping their identities as Matagi citizens a secret. Kamen Rider Super-1 must protect these children from the Dogma Kingdom, as they hold the secret to the Flying Dragon Fortress' weakness.

The prehistoric Croods family live in a particularly dangerous moment in time. Patriarch Grug, his mate Ugga, teenage daughter Eep, son Thunk, and feisty Gran gather food by day and huddle together in a cave at night. When a more evolved caveman named Guy arrives on the scene, Grug is distrustful, but it soon becomes apparent that Guy is correct about the impending destruction of their world.

Searching for a safer habitat, the prehistoric Crood family discovers an idyllic, walled-in paradise that meets all of its needs. Unfortunately, they must also learn to live with the Bettermans -- a family that's a couple of steps above the Croods on the evolutionary ladder. As tensions between the new neighbors start to rise, a new threat soon propels both clans on an epic adventure that forces them to embrace their differences, draw strength from one another, and survive together.

name: The Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild

info.plot: The fearless one-eyed weasel Buck teams up with mischievous possum brothers Crash & Eddie as they head off on a new adventure into Buck's home: The Dinosaur World.

Bob Parr has given up his superhero days to log in time as an insurance adjuster and raise his three children with his formerly heroic wife in suburbia. But when he receives a mysterious assignment, it's time to get back into costume.
A quirky, dysfunctional family's road trip is upended when they find themselves in the middle of the robot apocalypse and suddenly become humanity's unlikeliest last hope.

Teenage outsider Adam sets out on an epic and daring quest to uncover the mystery behind his long-lost dad, only to find out that he is none other than the legendary Bigfoot! He has been hiding deep in the forest for years to protect himself and his family from HairCo., a giant corporation eager to run scientific experiments with his special DNA. As father and son start making up for lost time after the boy's initial disbelief, Adam soon discovers that he too is gifted with superpowers beyond his imagination. But little do they know, HairCo. is on their tail as Adam's traces have led them to Bigfoot!

name: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge on the Run

info.plot: When his best friend Gary is suddenly snatched away, SpongeBob takes Patrick on a madcap mission far beyond Bikini Bottom to save their pink-shelled pal.

name: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water

info.plot: Burger Beard is a pirate who is in search of the final page of a magical book that makes any evil plan he writes in it come true, which happens to be the Krabby Patty secret formula. When the entire city of Bikini Bottom is put in danger, SpongeBob, Patrick, Mr. Krabs, Squidward, Sandy, and Plankton need to go on a quest that takes them to the surface. In order to get back the recipe and save their city, the gang must retrieve the book and transform themselves into superheroes.

Queen Poppy and Branch make a surprising discovery — there are other Troll worlds beyond their own, and their distinct differences create big clashes between these various tribes. When a mysterious threat puts all of the Trolls across the land in danger, Poppy, Branch, and their band of friends must embark on an epic quest to create harmony among the feuding Trolls to unite them against certain doom.
When alien invaders capture Earth's superheroes, their kids must learn to work together to save their parents - and the planet.

name: Birth of the 10th! Kamen Riders All Together!!: Kamen Rider ZX

info.plot: Ryo Murasame is an aircraft pilot, one day he was taking his sister out on a ride along the Amazon when they were shot down by an UFO. They survived, captured by the Badan Empire with his sister killed while Ryo became the Combat Roid known as ZX. His memory is erased by the Badan Empire and worked as their agent of evil. This does not last long as an accident occurs which causes Ryo to regain his memory and escapes Badan. A year later, Ryo begins his attack on Badan as they finish the preparations on their doomsday weapon: the Space Break System. However, a coordinated attack by the Kamen Riders disables the Badancium 84 supplies needed for Space System to work When Ryo arrives, he thinks Kamen Rider V3, Riderman and Kamen Rider Super-1 are enemies until they get him to listen as only one truck full of Badancium 84 makes it to the Badan's base run by Ambassador Darkness.
This is the  story of six married men in a village who wish  to break their fast and decide to hide their unlawful acts out of their wives' knowledge.

A sequel of 16 Puasa, this is a comedic story of six bumbling friends who constantly face difficulties fasting during the month of Ramadan. Working together, they always find ways to consume their midday meals - but not this time! They were sent to visit Tanjung Rambutan Hospital for Rashid's health, where they face many obstacles that prevent them from eating - including bumping into a hearse that reminds them of the end of time.

name: The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim

info.plot: A sudden attack by Wulf, a clever and traitorous lord of Rohan seeking vengeance for the death of his father, forces Helm Hammerhand, the King of Rohan, and his people to make a daring last stand in the ancient stronghold of the Hornburg.

A group of criminals kidnap a teenage ballet dancer, the daughter of a notorious gang leader, in order to obtain a ransom of $50 million, but over time, they discover that she is not just an ordinary girl. After the kidnappers begin to diminish, one by one, they discover, to their increasing horror, that they are locked inside with no normal little girl.

In order to pay the debt, Effa is willing to pretend to be an ustazah and lie about her background.

However, because he was busy being chased by loan shark, he decided to escape to Kampung Ramadan and met Imam Asyraf, an influencer who went viral because of his melodious voice when reciting.

Imam Asyraf has been appointed by Tok Jamlus to be an imam throughout this Ramadan tarawikh. Effa's presence in the village made Asyraf start to suspect something.
Ustazah Scammer debut
Season Finale

The Targaryen dynasty is at the absolute apex of its power, with more than 15 dragons under their yoke. Most empires crumble from such heights. In the case of the Targaryens, their slow fall begins when King Viserys breaks with a century of tradition by naming his daughter Rhaenyra heir to the Iron Throne. But when Viserys later fathers a son, the court is shocked when Rhaenyra retains her status as his heir, and seeds of division sow friction across the realm.
Viserys hosts a tournament to celebrate the birth of his second child. Rhaenyra welcomes her uncle Daemon back to the Red Keep.

Princess Rhaenyra dives deep into the prophecies about House Targaryen while confronting a realm that resists the idea of a woman on the Iron Throne, and Prince Daemon, embittered over being passed over as the heir to Westeros, prepares to go to war.
Daemon and the Sea Snake battle the Crabfeeder. The realm celebrates Aegon's second nameday. Rhaenyra faces the prospect of marriage.
Daemon returns to court after the successful completion of the battle. Princess Rhaenyra must deal with potential suitors in order to keep her line of succession.
Daemon visits his wife in the Vale. Viserys and Rhaenyra broker agreements with the Valeryons. Alicent seeks the truth about the princess.
Ten years later. Rhaenyra navigates Alicent's continued speculation about her children, while Daemon and Laena weigh an offer in Pentos.
As the families gather on Driftmark for a funeral, Viserys calls for an end to infighting and Alicent demands justice.
Six years later. With the Driftmark succession suddenly critical, Rhaenyra attempts to strike a bargain with Rhaenys.
While Alicent enlists Cole and Aemond to track down Aegon, Otto gathers the great houses of Westeros to affirm their allegiance.
Mourning a tragic death, Rhaenyra tries to hold the kingdom together and Daemon prepares for war.

While Rhaenyra struggles to come to terms with her son's murder, in King's Landing, Alicent grows concerned that Aegon's Small Council may lead them to an all-out war. Larys suggests Aegon needs a new Hand, and Rhaenyra arrives at a fateful decision.
As Otto schemes to turn the public against her, Rhaenyra questions Daemon's loyalty. Meanwhile, Ser Criston Cole concocts a misguided plan for revenge.

As ancient grudges resurface, Rhaenys suggests that Alicent may see reason while the men around her seek bloodshed. Ser Criston proposes a bold scheme. Daemon arrives at Harrenhal to raise an army for the Blacks.

episodes.name: The Red Dragon and the Gold

info.plot: In Rhaenyra's absence and with no word from Daemon at Harrenhal, Rhaenys tries to keep the peace on the Black Council as Cole mounts a campaign into the Crownlands. In King's Landing, Aemond continues to undermine Aegon's fragile hold on authority.

Amid whispers of bad omens, the Greens consider how to fill a void on Aegon's Council, Jacaerys sets out on a rogue mission to strike a deal, and Daemon enlists Lord Willem Blackwood to help persuade the Brackens to bend the knee.

With few options left, Rhaenyra summons a trusted knight for a risky venture and plots with Mysaria to catalyze the smallfolk. Meanwhile, Daemon's unease grows, and Aemond takes steps to reshape the Green Council.
As Rhaenyra looks to gain an advantage by unusual means, Daemon pressures a young liege lord to raise up his bannermen.
As Aemond becomes more volatile, Larys plots an escape, and Alicent grows more concerned about Helaena's safety. Flush with new power, Rhaenyra looks to press her advantage.

An unrivalled and highly elusive lone assassin, the Jackal, makes his living carrying out hits for the highest fee. But following his latest kill, he meets his match in a tenacious British intelligence officer who starts to track down the Jackal in a thrilling cat-and-mouse chase across Europe, leaving destruction in its wake.
When an elite assassin carries out a kill, it catches the attention of an intelligence officer, who starts to hunt him down.
With his client backing out of payment, the Jackal's reputation is on the line, and he starts to plot his revenge.
Armed with the knowledge of his wayward client's identity, the Jackal tracks him down in Munich, determined to settle the score.
His vengeance fulfilled, the Jackal flees Munich and tries to quell Nuria's suspicions. Bianca follows a new lead in her hunt.
The Jackal visits Norman with a special commission... but with Bianca also tracking Norman down, she is starting to close in on him.
Following his shootout with Bianca, the Jackal must escape his captors and regroup ahead of his next hit, as Bianca follows his trail.
The Jackal and Bianca head to Tallinn before UDC's announcement. The Jackal must use all his wiles as he prepares to take his shot.
Bianca gains insight into a secret file. She learns the true identity of the Jackal and how he became a contract killer.
With the release of River imminent, UDC believes himself safe. As time runs out, the Jackal must use all his skills to reach his target.
A wanted man, the Jackal is on the run, desperate to get back to Nuria, but Bianca is given one last shot to bring him to justice.
The people of Mangollai village like Colochi Saami and Saamikannu opposed education for the poor while people like Annadurai and Sivangaanam fought against oppression.
A Young boy who has a close bond with an elephant since his childhood. Later, as he grows up, a powerful politician who is envious of him creates problems.

Becky and Jim are married but are having troubles. So they head to a remote couple's retreat to try and save their marriage. They end up going with their friends who are coupled up as well with issues. However, the couples retreat is not all it seems when accusations are made, someone goes missing, and another is found dead.

A SWAT captain is permanently injured during a failed assignment and must retire. Although depressed, his daughter gives him hope, and he slowly begins to adjust to his new life. When she is kidnapped by human traffickers, he must track her down using every remaining sense and save her in this blind battle of life and death.
Three short films about the hidden horrors that lurk behind the urban landscape of Hong Kong.

Jeff Mitchell seems to have it all. He has an interesting and lucrative job, a loving wife, and two amazing kids. Therefore, life is good. However, on one bright day, a cosmic sucker punch comes out of the blue. When Jeff was in high school, unbeknownst to him, he got his girlfriend pregnant. Next, the girl moved away, had the baby, and raised her as a single mother, never telling her daughter, Carlee, who her real father was. However, Carlee's mother recently died in a tragic accident, prompting Carlee to try and uncover the truth. Maybe Jeff is not so lucky after all?

In the underground racing scene, emerging racer Xiao Le spirals into despair after an accident during a race with his brother, A Chieh. His life changes when he meets doctor Hui-Hui and becomes an ambulance driver, vowing to save people with speed. However, fate complicates things as San Pao and underground racing leader Brother Ben investigate, uncovering the unexpected truth about A Chieh.
After their late former Captain is framed, Lowrey and Burnett try to clear his name, only to end up on the run themselves.

Living a bleak existence at a London orphanage, 12-year-old Peter finds himself whisked away to the fantastical world of Neverland. Adventure awaits as he meets new friend James Hook and the warrior Tiger Lily. They must band together to save Neverland from the ruthless pirate Blackbeard. Along the way, the rebellious and mischievous boy discovers his true destiny, becoming the hero forever known as Peter Pan.

Criminal mastermind Mason is about to execute the score of a lifetime when his lover and key member of his crew, Decker, takes the team down and reveals she’s an undercover Interpol agent. Heartbroken, Mason escapes and retires from the life of crime until his younger brother Shawn is out of his league taking on a big bank heist all on his own. Mason has no choice left but to come to the rescue, while Interpol brings Decker in hoping to unnerve him. Before the SWAT teams storm the bank, Mason must use every tool in his arsenal to not only escape with the prize, but also the love of his life.

Mufasa, a cub lost and alone, meets a sympathetic lion named Taka, the heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of a group of misfits searching for their destiny.

Two highly trained operatives grow close from a distance after being sent to guard opposite sides of a mysterious gorge. When an evil below emerges, they must work together to survive what lies within.

The 2025 Elimination Chamber (known as Elimination Chamber: Toronto) was the 15th Elimination Chamber professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) and livestreaming event produced by WWE. It was held for wrestlers from the promotion's Raw and SmackDown brand divisions. The event took place on Saturday, March 1, 2025, at Rogers Centre in Toronto, Ontario, Canada.

After meeting with newly elected U.S. President Thaddeus Ross, Sam finds himself in the middle of an international incident. He must discover the reason behind a nefarious global plot before the true mastermind has the entire world seeing red.

In the land of Oz, ostracized and misunderstood green-skinned Elphaba is forced to share a room with the popular aristocrat Glinda at Shiz University, and the two's unlikely friendship is tested as they begin to fulfill their respective destinies as Glinda the Good and the Wicked Witch of the West.

Kraven Kravinoff's complex relationship with his ruthless gangster father, Nikolai, starts him down a path of vengeance with brutal consequences, motivating him to become not only the greatest hunter in the world, but also one of its most feared.

Years after witnessing the death of the revered hero Maximus at the hands of his uncle, Lucius is forced to enter the Colosseum after his home is conquered by the tyrannical Emperors who now lead Rome with an iron fist. With rage in his heart and the future of the Empire at stake, Lucius must look to his past to find strength and honor to return the glory of Rome to its people.
An airport security officer races to outsmart a mysterious traveler forcing him to let a dangerous item slip onto a Christmas Eve flight.

With his marriage fraying, Blake persuades his wife Charlotte to take a break from the city and visit his remote childhood home in rural Oregon. As they arrive at the farmhouse in the dead of night, they're attacked by an unseen animal and barricade themselves inside the home as the creature prowls the perimeter. But as the night stretches on, Blake begins to behave strangely, transforming into something unrecognizable.

A realtor is pulled back into the life he left behind after his former partner-in-crime resurfaces with an ominous message. With his crime-lord brother also on his trail, he must confront his past and the history he never fully buried.

Powered with incredible speed, Sonic The Hedgehog embraces his new home on Earth. That is, until Sonic sparks the attention of super-uncool evil genius Dr. Robotnik. Now it’s super-villain vs. super-sonic in an all-out race across the globe to stop Robotnik from using Sonic’s unique power for world domination.

Sonic, Knuckles, and Tails reunite against a powerful new adversary, Shadow, a mysterious villain with powers unlike anything they have faced before. With their abilities outmatched in every way, Team Sonic must seek out an unlikely alliance in hopes of stopping Shadow and protecting the planet.
The Doctor and his companion travel across time and space encountering incredible friends and foes.
Ruby learns the Doctor's amazing secrets when he takes her to the far future. There, they find a baby farm run by babies. But can they be saved from the terrifying bogeyman?
The Doctor and Ruby meet The Beatles but discover that the all-powerful Maestro is changing history. London becomes a battleground with the future of humanity at stake.
Caught in the middle of a devastating war on Kastarion 3, the Doctor is trapped when he steps on a landmine. Can he save himself and Ruby, plus the entire planet... without moving?
Landing on the Welsh coast, the Doctor and Ruby embark on the strangest journey of their lives. In a rain-lashed pub, the locals sit in fear of ancient legends coming to life.
The world of Finetime seems happy and harmonious. But an awful terror is preying on the citizens. Can the Doctor and Ruby make them see the truth before it’s too late?
The Doctor and Ruby land in 1813, where guests at a duchess's party are being murdered and a mysterious bounty hunter called Rogue is about to change the Doctor's life forever.
The Doctor and UNIT investigate Ruby's past. But as the Time Window reveals horrifying secrets from Christmas Eve, the mysterious Triad Technology unleash the greatest evil of all.
The Doctor has lost, his ageless enemy reigns supreme, and a shadow is falling over creation. Nothing can stop the devastation... except, perhaps, one woman.

Willis Wu, a background character trapped in a police procedural, tries to find his way into the larger story–and along the way discovers secrets about the strange world he inhabits and his family's buried history.
A Chinatown waiter finds himself in a mystery.
Willis figures out where he fits into the story.
Willis tries to level up. Lana tries to keep her job by kissing up to Green.
Willis and Lana get closer. Willis uncovers family secrets. Fatty finds a new role at the restaurant.
You can't go home again.
There's something very wrong with this place.
Willis gets a new partner. Lana gets a new partner. The show gets a new theme song.
Advertising is based on one thing: happiness.
Lana gets an unexpected message. Willis gets a promotion.
Willis tries to write his own ending.

name: Mickey and the Very Many Christmases

info.plot: Mickey makes a magical wish that every day could be Christmas — but winds up having second thoughts when his wish actually comes true!

During World War II, the US Army's only all-Black, all-women battalion takes on an impossible mission: sorting through a three-year backlog of 17 million pieces of mail that hadn't been delivered to American soldiers and finish within six months.

When Steven Grant, a mild-mannered gift-shop employee, becomes plagued with blackouts and memories of another life, he discovers he has dissociative identity disorder and shares a body with mercenary Marc Spector. As Steven/Marc’s enemies converge upon them, they must navigate their complex identities while thrust into a deadly mystery among the powerful gods of Egypt.
Steven Grant, a mild-mannered man who works a mundane job, begins to suspect that his life may not be his own when an alter living inside him begins to emerge.
As Steven reels from the fact that his life may not be his own, a mysterious partner emerges from the past as a war of the gods looms on the horizon.
With Marc in the forefront and Harrow near Ammit’s tomb, Marc needs to navigate Cairo while putting his differences aside with Layla and Steven without jeopardizing their mission.
Marc & Steven trek the Siwa Desert with Layla to find Ammit’s tomb, but the threats ahead look to protect the goddess’ resting place.
Marc & Steven search through their memories to find their truth or become left behind.
With Layla tracking down Harrow, Marc, Steven, and Khonshu must return to Cairo to stop Ammit as she looks to threaten humanity once more.

The story of haves and have-nots in a world in which there’s almost nothing left to have. 200 years after the apocalypse, the gentle denizens of luxury fallout shelters are forced to return to the irradiated hellscape their ancestors left behind — and are shocked to discover an incredibly complex, gleefully weird, and highly violent universe waiting for them.
Okey dokey...
I know life can't have been easy up here…
The Wasteland's got its own Golden Rule…
Death to Management.
Everyone wants to save the world…
What happens when the ranchers have more power than the Sheriff?
Every generation has their own dumbass ideas…
War…

In Japan in the year 1600, at the dawn of a century-defining civil war, Lord Yoshii Toranaga is fighting for his life as his enemies on the Council of Regents unite against him, when a mysterious European ship is found marooned in a nearby fishing village.
Destinies converge in Japan after a barbarian ship washes ashore in a poor fishing village. Meanwhile, in Osaka, Lord Toranaga finds himself outplayed by his enemies.
Blackthorne's arrival in Osaka stirs up a hornet's nest of rivalries. Mariko is trapped between her cause and her faith when she must translate for the barbarian in Lord Toranaga's custody.
After Blackthorne survives a brazen assassination attempt, Toranaga realizes he must ferry his allies out of Osaka or risk certain defeat.
Blackthorne and Mariko test their new alliance as they train Toranaga's gun regiment for war. Yabushige must navigate his past promises to Ishido when an old friend comes to the village.
Blackthorne and Mariko struggle to contain the secret that could get them both killed. Yabushige searches for the spy who has betrayed his intentions to Lord Toranaga.
Lady Ochiba returns to Osaka in order to accelerate the Regents' campaign against Toranaga. In Ajiro, Toranaga tests Mariko's loyalty to his cause.
Outplayed by new alliances in Osaka, Toranaga is forced to carve out a new deal with a long lost family member.

Toranaga's defeated clan moves to Edo and awaits their fate. Blackthorne must decide who he fights for - the lord who has turned his back on him, or the ambition that brought him to Japan in the first place.
Mariko arrives in Osaka for the fight of her life. Blackthorne and Yabushige scramble to save their own heads as their options dwindle.
In the wake of a tragic death, Blackthorne finally considers the true nature of Toranaga's plan.
When a powerful spell turns her parents into giant monsters, a teenage princess must journey into the wild to reverse the curse before it's too late.
The crafty Bad Guys crew embarks on a high-stakes Halloween heist to swipe a priceless amulet from a spooky mansion. What could go wrong?
Plankton's tangled love story with his sentient computer wife goes sideways when she takes a stand — and decides to destroy the world without him.

Barbie stars as Blair Willows, a kind-hearted girl who is chosen to attend Princess Charm School: a magical, modern place that teaches dancing, how to have tea parties, and proper princess manners. Blair loves her classes -- as well as the helpful magical sprites and her new friends, Princesses Hadley and Isla. But when royal teacher Dame Devin discovers that Blair looks a lot like the kingdom’s missing princess, she turns Blair’s world upside down to stop her from claiming the throne. Now Blair, Hadley and Delancy must find an enchanted crown to prove Blair’s true identity in this charming and magical princess story!

Precocious tween Karin finds herself abandoned by her father in rural Japan. Living in a temple with her grandfather, she meets Anzu, a giant "ghost cat" and notorious layabout tasked with looking after her. Distrustful of her new guardian, Karin sabotages Anzu's odd jobs for the townsfolk and befriends the eccentric local forest spirits. In an effort to win Karin over, Anzu accidentally makes a deal with the devil, and all Hell breaks loose.

In a society devastated by the effects of an all-out war between heroes and villains, a mysterious giant fortress suddenly appears, engulfing towns and people one after another. Then, a man reminiscent of All Might, the 'symbol of peace', stands in front of Izuku and his friends...

In another dimension, the villainous scientist Duke of Zill, with the help of his mechanical, geometric army, ultimately takes over the golden kingdom of Oriana, where Duke has just escaped exile! But Felix the Cat must bravely save Princess Oriana and restore order once again, from her terrible Uncle Zill and his smoke-belching mechanical troops before he can put his sinister plot into action!

This collection of 11 short films produced by Illumination includes: From the "Despicable Me" franchise: Mower Minions (2016); Yellow Is the New Black (2018); Competition (2015); Cro Minion (2015); Binky Nelson Unpacified (2015); Panic in the Mailroom (2013). From the "Secret Life of Pets" franchise: Super Gidget (2019). From the "Sing" franchise: Eddie's Life Coach (2017); Gunter Babysits (2017). From the "Lorax" franchise: Serenade (2012); Wagon Ho! (2012).
Forcibly separated from her twin brother when they are orphaned, a melancholic misfit learns how to find confidence within herself amid the clutter of misfortunes and everyday life.

In this epic true story inspired by the legend of King Gesar, a young man grows up in exile in a world overrun by demons and monsters. When evil forces threaten his home, he returns to save his people and embrace his destiny as great hero and ruler.

The short film companion to Mac Miller's Balloonerism follows a group of school friends who are transfigured by the music of a chord organ and launched into a shadow world. Swallowed by the turtle of time, they must plod through the underbelly of adulthood.

name: Gracie & Pedro: Pets to the Rescue

info.plot: Family frenemies, Gracie and Pedro, must put their differences aside, embarking on a thrilling quest packed with perilous escapades in order to reunite with their owners.

name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Guardians of the Galaxy - The Thanos Threat

info.plot: The Guardians are on a mission to deliver the Build Stone to the Avengers before the Ravagers, Thanos and his underlings steal it from them.

name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Avengers Reassembled!

info.plot: The Avengers are forced to “party” with Ultron when he seeks to disassemble the team by taking control of Iron Man’s armor and enact a nefarious scheme to take over the world.

name: LEGO Marvel Avengers: Loki in Training

info.plot: Loki declares he wants to be an Avenger, so Iron Man decides to make Loki an "Avenger In Training." It's a great plan until Thanos arrives on Earth looking for Loki.

Shrek challenges Donkey, Puss in Boots and his other fairy tale character friends to spend the night in Lord Farquaad's haunted castle, telling scary stories to see who can resist becoming scared and stay the longest.
When Thanos steals the quantum tunnel, the Avengers embark on a mission to stop him from changing history.

11-year-old Alfonso, heir of Don Quixote, and his three imaginary musical rabbits are joined by Pancho and Victoria to save their beloved town of La Mancha from a huge storm, created by an evil corporation seeking to own the land.

When a faithful police dog and his human police officer owner are injured together on the job, a harebrained but life-saving surgery fuses the two of them together and Dog Man is born. Dog Man is sworn to protect and serve—and fetch, sit and roll over. As Dog Man embraces his new identity and strives to impress his Chief, he must stop the pretty evil plots of feline supervillain Petey the Cat.

name: The Day the Earth Blew Up: A Looney Tunes Movie

info.plot: Porky and Daffy, the classic animated odd couple, turn into unlikely heroes when their antics at the local bubble gum factory uncover a secret alien mind control plot. Against all odds, the two are determined to save their town (and the world!)...that is if they don't drive each other crazy in the process.

Hell – A place where beings that have committed mortal sins during their lifetime are sent. It is a realm where even Soul Reapers are forbidden to interfere. When a group of vicious Sinners plot to escape from this eternal prison, they discover that Substitute Soul Reaper Ichigo Kurosaki is the key to their freedom.
Oh takes it upon himself to introduce Christmas joy to his fellow Boovs. Unfortunately, his well-meaning mission nearly destroys the city.

name: Bleach the Movie: Memories of Nobody

info.plot: In Karakura Town, unidentifiable spirits begin appearing en mases. While attempting to deal with these strange souls, Ichigo Kurosaki and Rukia Kuchiki meet Senna, a mysterious shinigami who wipes out most of them. Senna refuses to answer any questions, so Ichigo is forced to follow her while Rukia tries to find out what's going on.

name: The Witcher: Sirens of the Deep

info.plot: Geralt of Rivia, a mutated monster hunter, is hired to investigate a series of attacks in a seaside village and finds himself drawn into a centuries-old conflict between humans and merpeople. He must count on friends — old and new — to solve the mystery before the hostilities between the two kingdoms escalate into an all-out war.

The Galaxy is being threatened by an cat robot that is very evil and an group known as the Space Guardians, an alien group of Superheros is tasked to stop it. And newest member of the Space Guardians, Squeak must join up with an old veteran, Ham Sanders to stop the evil cat-bot and prevent him from destroying the known universe and thereby save the day.

name: LEGO Hidden Side: Night of the Harbinger

info.plot: Jack and Parker work to seal a Hidden Side hole when a fire ghost escapes covered in a strange silvery substance and reveals that their world may be doomed.

name: Fox and Hare Save the Forest

info.plot: One day, Fox and Hare find that Owl has disappeared. Together with their friends, they search the forest to find him, but instead they discover a big lake that was not there before. Could the sudden appearance of the lake have anything to do with Owl’s disappearance? They must go and find Owl, who is somewhere out there on the rapidly rising water... It is the start of an exciting and fun adventure.

After receiving an unexpected call from her wayfinding ancestors, Moana journeys alongside Maui and a new crew to the far seas of Oceania and into dangerous, long-lost waters for an adventure unlike anything she's ever faced.

A pair of mice attempt to board Noah's Ark: Vini, a charismatic poet with terrible stage fright, and Tito, a talented and charming guitarist. When the rains come, only one male and one female of each species is allowed on Noah's Ark. With the help of an ingenious cockroach and fate's good luck, Vini and Tito sneak their way onto the Ark and together avert a showdown among the ships carnivores and plant eaters. All the while, the animals perform a series of classic songs inspired by world renowned poet, Vinicius de Moraes. Can these talented stowaways use music to break the tension and help these cooped up creatures survive the 40 days and 40 nights together?

Emma, a miniature human girl adopted by animal parents, yearns to find the truth about her human roots. But when she discovers a hidden island full of tiny humans, it's not the fairy tale she hoped for. Will she risk all she's ever known to uncover secrets from her past?

Gromit’s concern that Wallace is becoming too dependent on his inventions proves justified, when Wallace invents a “smart” gnome that seems to develop a mind of its own. When it emerges that a vengeful figure from the past might be masterminding things, it falls to Gromit to battle sinister forces and save his master… or Wallace may never be able to invent again!

Santa Claus's wish comes true when he accidentally bumps his head and starts believing he's SuperKlaus. With the help of Billie and Leo his elf-xecutive assistant, SuperKlaus will take on a toy-obsessed businessman to save Christmas.

name: Sirocco and the Kingdom of Winds

info.plot: Agnès, Juliette and Carmen's neighbour, writes children's storybooks that take place in a fantasy world, The Kingdom of the Winds. The intrepid sisters discover a passageway between their world and this extraordinary universe. Once on the other side the girls take on the appearance of cats, and discover Sirocco, a terrifying character who can control the wind.

Mary and Tom are parentless Irish siblings who arrive in New York City via ocean liner in 1886 and quickly find themselves on a wild, cross-country journey aboard a transcontinental "Orphan Train" where they meet an extraordinary new friend who will change their lives forever.
A pair of rival butterflies form an unlikely friendship.
A solitary cat, displaced by a great flood, finds refuge on a boat with various species and must navigate the challenges of adapting to a transformed world together.
